uiem%20for%20Rashid%20Khan%3A%20The%20Finest%20'Khayal'%20Vocalist%20Knows%20No%20Language%20Other%20Than%20Music%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F02182754%2FEffect-95.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20a%20perpetually%20unhappy%2013-year-old.%20I%20was%20losing%20faith.%20I%20had%20somewhat%20discovered%20nihilistic%20writers%2C%20but%20I%20also%20loved%20Marx.%20And%20I%20romanticized%20a%20country%20that%20no%20longer%20existed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%2C%20we%20were%20never%20formally%20introduced%20to%20music.%20With%20the%20exception%20of%20a%20mini%20Casio%20keyboard%20that%20my%20father%20gifted%20me%20when%20I%20was%20quite%20young%2C%20I%20have%20no%20childhood%20musical%20memories.%20The%20keyboard%20had%20pre-recorded%20melodies%20in%20its%20%E2%80%9CSong%20Bank%E2%80%9D.%20While%20randomly%20listening%20to%20them%20%E2%80%94%20as%20I%20cheerfully%20pretended%20to%20play%20the%20keys%20%E2%80%94%20I%20always%20wondered%20why%20would%20certain%20melodies%20sadden%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESadness%2C%20in%20our%20home%2C%20was%20always%20tied%20to%20words.%20How%20could%20something%20wordless%2C%20after%20all%2C%20make%20me%20feel%20sad%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20not%20that%20no%20one%20liked%20music%20at%20home.%20There%20were%2C%20of%20course%2C%20old%20Bollywood%20and%20Pakistani%20songs%2C%20as%20well%20as%20ghazals%20by%20iconic%20artists%2C%20to%20a%20certain%20extent.%20However%2C%20the%20latter%20were%20always%20appreciated%20solely%20for%20their%20lyrical%20material.%20Ghazal%20singers%20were%20often%20judged%20whenever%20they%20mispronounced%20any%20Urdu%20words.%20All%20the%20praise%20belonged%20to%20the%20poets%20alone.%20I%20remember%20once%20my%20mother%20politely%2C%20and%20rightly%2C%20told%20me%20it%20was%20really%20embarrassing%20not%20to%20remember%20the%20words%20accurately%20while%20quoting%20a%20poet.%20I%20must%20have%20forgotten%20a%20couplet