EWhy%20are%20we%20expected%20to%20visibly%20grieve%20only%20the%20ones%20close%20to%20us%3F%20In%20the%20absence%20of%20any%20rituals%2C%20how%20do%20I%20grieve%20someone%20I%20had%20never%20physically%20met%2C%20or%20even%20tried%20to%20contact%2C%20and%20yet%20who%20played%20a%20profound%20role%20in%20my%20emotional%2C%20or%2C%20dare%20I%20say%2C%20spiritual%20life%20through%20his%20art%3F%20To%20me%2C%20Ustad%20Rashid%20Khan%20was%20the%20living%20embodiment%20of%20the%20Khayal.%20Now%2C%20hardly%20a%20day%20after%20his%20death%2C%20when%20I%20think%20this%2C%20I%20find%20myself%20surprised%20that%20I%20lived%20in%20the%20times%20of%20Rashid%20Khan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20often%20known%20in%20the%20classical%20music%20fraternity%20to%20be%20the%20finest%20Khayal%20vocalist%20of%20his%20generation.%20With%20his%20passing%2C%20without%20leaving%20behind%20any%20significantly%20trained%2C%20or%2C%20at%20least%2C%20known%20disciples%20in%20his%20tradition%20and%20signature%20style%2C%20a%20strange%20fear%20has%20arrested%20me.%20Are%20we%20witnessing%20the%20death%20of%20the%20genre%3F%20I%20am%20reminded%20of%20C.S.%20Lewis%E2%80%99s%20poignant%20exploration%20of%20grief%20in%20%3Cem%3EA%20Grief%3C%2Fem%3E%20Observed%3A%20%E2%80%9CNo%20one%20ever%20told%20me%20that%20grief%20felt%20so%20like%20fear.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tradition%20of%20the%20Khayal%20gives%20a%20lot%20of%20importance%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3Ealaap%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20rhythmless%20exploration%20of%20the%20raga%2C%20unfolding%20its%20emotional%20nectar%2C%20the%20rasa%2C%20by%20creatively%20improvising%20phrases%20within%20the%20fixed%20structure.%20This%20structure%20relies%20on%20the%20ascending%20and%20descending%20order%20of%20notes%2C%20prominent%20notes%2C%20among%20other%20things.%20The%20%3Cem%3Ealaap%3C%2Fem%3E%20leads%20to%20a%20structured%20composition%2C%20known%20as%20%3Cem%3Ebandish%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20set%20to%20a%20certain%20rhythm%20cycle%20in%20%3Cem%3Evilambit%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20slow%20tempo.%20The%20performance%20culminates%20with%20fast%20tempo%2C%20known%20as%20%3Cem%3Edrut%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20in%20which%20an%20artist%20expresses%20their%20virtuosity%20and%20complex%20understanding%20of%20the%20rhythm%2C%20demonstrating%20their%20vocal%20ability%20by%20singing%20various%20sorts%20of%20%3Cem%3Etaans%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Epaltas%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20so%20on.%20These%20formal%20intricacies%2C%20however%2C%20are%20pleasing%20to%20the%20ear%20only%20if%20the%20raga%20comes%20into%20being%20%E2%80%94%20if%20its%20essence%2C%20%3Cem%3Erachao%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20is%20established%2C%20in%20the%20seemingly%20formless%20improvisations%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Ealaap%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20great%20pain%2C%E2%80%9D%20writes%20Emily%20Dickinson%2C%20%E2%80%9Ca%20formal%20feeling%20comes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERashid%20Khan%20really%20knew%20how%20to%20awaken%20a%20raga%20through%20his%20%3Cem%3Ealaap%3C%2Fem%3E.%20As%20traditional%20musicians%20in%20Lahore%20often%20say%20while%20praising%20the%20artists%20of%20yesteryears%2C%20ragas%20could%20be%20felt%20in%20physical%20form%20when%20certain%20artists%20sang%20them.%20In%20such%20%3Cem%3Ebaithaks%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20we%20are%20told%2C%20the%20presence%20of%20ragas%20as%20beings%20would%20be%20undeniable.%20Although%20I%20was%20not%20fortunate%20enough%20to%20experience%20him%20live%2C%20I%20have%20met%20many%20ragas%20in%20my%20room%20through%20the%20recordings%20of%20the%20great%20Khan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELastly%2C%20why%20does%20death%20feel%20so%20shocking%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20certain%20people%3F%20Why%20do%20we%20assume%20some%20people%20to%20be%20eternal%3F%20What%20does%20it%20mean%20for%20an%20artist%20to%20die%20at%20the%20peak%20of%20their%20career%3F%20Jaun%20Elia%20in%20an%20elegy-poem%20written%20for%20a%20poet%20friend%20wishes%20his%20friend%E2%80%99s%20grave%20to%20be%20filled%20with%20light%20so%20that%20he%20can%20write.%20In%20some%20sources%20of%20Islamic%20eschatology%2C%20angels%20are%20said%20to%20visit%20the%20fresh%20grave%20once%20the%20funeral%20and%20burial%20is%20over%2C%20and%20interact%20with%20the%20deceased%20in%20the%20language%20they%20spoke%20while%20being%20alive.%20This%20time%20it%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20easy%20for%20the%20celestial%20beings%2C%20for%20Rashid%20Khan%20knows%20no%20language%20other%20than%20music.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAmmar%20Aziz%20is%20a%20poet%20from%20Lahore.%20His%20debut%20book%20%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20Missing%20Prayer%3Cem%3E%20is%20forthcoming%20in%202024.%20He%20is%20officially%20selecting%20and%20translating%20the%20works%20of%20the%20Urdu%20poet%20Jaun%20Elia.%20He%20can%20be%20reached%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aammar.aziz%40me.com%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Eammar.aziz%40me.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706931037000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F02182754%2FEffect-95.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Frequiem-for-rashid-khan-the-finest-khayal-vocalist-knows-no-language-other-than-music%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Ustad%20was%20a%20living%20embodiment%20to%20the%20tradition%20of%20Khayal%2C%20which%20gives%20importance%20to%20the%20alaap%2C%20a%20rhythmless%20exploration%20of%20the%20raga%2C%20unfolding%20its%20emotional%20nectar%2C%20the%20rasa%2C%20by%20creatively%20improvising%20phrases%20within%20the%20fixed%20structure.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Frequiem-for-rashid-khan-the-finest-khayal-vocalist-knows-no-language-other-than-music%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mushy%20pics%20of%20Rakul%20Preet%20Singh-Jackky%20Bhagnani%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706931000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107371161%2Cimgsize-70204.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesof