0Facebook%20groups%20are%20where%20I'm%20picking%20up%20advice%2C%20opportunities%2C%20and%20a%20network%20of%20people%20to%20learn%20from%20in%20the%20online%20business%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EBuilding%20parenting%20communities%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Woman%20on%20beach%20with%20two%20children%20in%20Spain%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65bd70c343bb77284ba3497f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAuthor%20on%20the%20beach%20in%20Spain%20with%20her%20two%20sons.%3Cp%3ENicola%20Prentis%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20moved%20to%20Girona%2C%20a%20city%20in%20Spain%20where%20I%20knew%20no%20one%2C%20I%20made%20friends%20and%20sought%20advice%20via%20parent%20groups%2C%20often%20canvassing%20for%20answers%20to%20logistical%20questions%20in%20bigger%20Barcelona%20and%20Madrid%20groups%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Girona%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20a%20freelancer%20in%20Spain%20is%20monstrously%20complex%2C%20with%20millions%20of%20rules%20and%20implications%20for%20tax%20and%20social%20security.%20The%20advice%20I%20get%20from%20Facebook%20groups%20is%20often%20better%20and%20faster%20than%20I%20get%20from%20the%20accountant%20I%20have%20on%20retainer.%20Sometimes%2C%20my%20Facebook%20expat%20network%20and%20work%20collide%2C%20like%20the%20time%20I%20bought%20a%20secondhand%20kids'%20bike%2C%20and%20the%20seller's%20husband%20became%20my%20favorite%20content%20writing%20client%20ever.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFacebook%20brings%20out%20the%20connectors%20in%20any%20field%2C%20those%20people%20who%20genuinely%20enjoy%20bringing%20people%20together%20and%20to%20whom%20I'm%20forever%20grateful%20as%20I'm%20a%20fully%20paid-up%20introvert.%20My%20local%20%26quot%3Bmamas%20and%20papas%26quot%3B%20group%20is%20co-hosted%20by%20an%20amazing%20woman%20who%20regularly%20holds%20family%20meetups.%20She's%20just%20about%20to%20cater%20to%20that%20other%20hard-to-navigate%20need%2C%20dating%20as%20a%20foreigner%20who's%20been%20burned%20out%20by%20Tinder%2C%20with%20a%20speed%20dating%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ELooking%20for%20love%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Ffacebook-dating%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erelationships%2C%20Facebook%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20played%20a%20helping%20hand.%20Gone%20are%20the%20days%20when%20that%20cutie%20you%20lost%20contact%20with%20became%20a%20%26quot%3BWhat%20if%3F%26quot%3B%20Like%2C%20Tobey%2C%20the%20tall%2C%20good-looking%20German%20engineer%20I%20English%20tutored%20in%20the%20Yellow%20Submarine%20hostel%20in%20Brisbane%20in%202003.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20I%20wasn't%20ready%20to%20date%20as%20I%20was%20getting%20over%20another%20heartbreak.%20That%20was%20the%20year%20before%20Facebook%20launched.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20my%20comment%20on%20the%20photo%20of%20a%20family%20friend%20I%20hadn't%20seen%20for%20over%2010%20years%20led%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcouple-scheduled-first-kiss-on-google-calendar-took-away-anxiety-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshort%20but%20on-the-brink-of-serious%20relationship%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20I'm%20just%20about%20to%20visit%20an%20ex%20in%20Australia%20from%2021%20years%20ago.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20I'd%20looked%20him%20up%20without%20success%20and%20recently%20spotted%20someone%20else%20tagging%20him%20in%20a%20local%20news%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I%20moved%20again%2C%20I'd%20join%20a%20few%20Facebook%20local%20groups%20with%20the%20word%20%26quot%3Bexpat.%26quot%3B%20Then%20I'd%20look%20for%20more%20nuanced%20groups%20to%20fit%20with%20being%20a%20parent%2C%20or%20hobbies%20and%20work%2C%20knowing%20I'd%20have%20instant%20connections%2C%20advice%2C%20and%20pre-made%20friends%20when%20I%20arrived.%20Facebook%20makes%20it%20possible%20to%20slot%20in%20as%20if%20you've%20already%20