of%20a%20larger%20retaliatory%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20initial%20news%20broke%2C%20US%20Central%20Command%2C%20or%20CENTCOM%2C%20released%20a%20statement%20that%20said%20numerous%20aircraft%2C%20including%20long-ranger%20bombers%2C%20conducted%20airstrikes%20against%20Iran's%20Islamic%20Revolutionary%20Guards%20Corps%20(IRGC)%20Quds%20Force%20and%20affiliated%20militia%20groups%20in%20Iraq%20and%20Syria.%20It%20said%20more%20than%20125%20precision%20munitions%20were%20used%20to%20hit%20over%2085%20targets%20in%20the%20two%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20facilities%20that%20were%20struck%20included%20command%20and%20control%20operations%20centers%2C%20intelligence%20centers%2C%20rockets%2C%20and%20missiles%2C%20and%20unmanned%20aerial%20vehicle%20storages%2C%20and%20logistics%20and%20munition%20supply%20chain%20facilities%20of%20militia%20groups%20and%20their%20IRGC%20sponsors%20who%20facilitated%20attacks%20against%20US%20and%20Coalition%20forces%2C%26quot%3B%20CENTCOM%20said%20in%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FCENTCOM%2Fstatus%2F1753533250146824348%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhite%20House%20National%20Security%20Council%20spokesperson%20John%20Kirby%20told%20reporters%20that%20the%20strikes%20hit%20seven%20facilities%20used%20by%20the%20IRGC%20and%20affiliated%20militia%20groups%20in%20Iraq%20and%20Syria%2C%20and%20the%20military%20action%20lasted%2030%20minutes.%20The%20number%20of%20casualties%20is%20unclear%2C%20but%20he%20said%20the%20strikes%20are%20believed%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bsuccessful.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPresident%20Joe%20Biden%20said%20that%20while%20the%20US%20response%20began%20on%20Friday%2C%20%26quot%3Bit%20will%20continue%20at%20times%20and%20places%20of%20our%20choosing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20United%20States%20does%20not%20seek%20conflict%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20or%20anywhere%20else%20in%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fbriefing-room%2Fstatements-releases%2F2024%2F02%2F02%2Fstatement-from-president-joe-biden-on-u-s-military-operation-in-the-middle-east%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%26quot%3BBut%20let%20all%20those%20who%20might%20seek%20to%20do%20us%20harm%20know%20this%3A%20If%20you%20harm%20an%20American%2C%20we%20will%20respond.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20retaliatory%20action%20comes%20days%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fenemy-drone-killed-us-troops-jordan-slipped-past-defenses-report-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ea%20drone%20struck%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20small%20US%20military%20outpost%20in%20northeast%20Jordan.%20It%20struck%20the%20living%20quarters%20for%20American%20troops%2C%20killing%20three%20and%20injuring%20dozens%2C%20some%20of%20whom%20had%20to%20be%20evacuated%20from%20the%20country%20to%20higher%20level%20care.%20The%20Pentagon%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.centcom.mil%2FMEDIA%2FPRESS-RELEASES%2FPress-Release-View%2FArticle%2F3658552%2Fupdate-us-casualties-in-northeast-jordan-near-syrian-border%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Esaid%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20aftermath%20that%20it%20expected%20the%20number%20of%20wounded%20individuals%20to%20fluctuate%20as%20people%20seek%20follow-on%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20House%20immediately%20blamed%20Iran-backed%20militias%20for%20the%20deadly%20incident%20and%20vowed%20revenge.%20%26quot%3BHave%20no%20doubt%20%E2%80%94%20we%20will%20hold%20all%20those%20responsible%2C%26quot%3B%20Biden%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fbriefing-room%2Fstatements-releases%2F2024%2F01%2F28%2Fstatement-from-president-joe-biden-on-attack-on-u-s-service-members-in-northeastern-jordan-near-the-syria-border%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Esaid%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEchoing%20Biden's%20remarks%2C%20Secretary%20of%20Defense%20Lloyd%20Austin%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.defense.gov%2FNews%2FReleases%2FRelease%2FArticle%2F3658472%2Fstatement-from-secretary-of-defense-lloyd-j-austin-iii-on-an-attack-against-us%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26quot%3Bthe%20President%20and%20I%20will%20not%20tolerate%20attacks%20on%20American%20forces%2C%20and%20we%20will%20take%20all%20necessary%20actions%20to%20defend%20the%20United%20States%2C%20our%20troops%2C%20and%20our%20interests.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWashington%20also%20signaled%20throughout%20the%20week%20that%20there%20won't%20be%20a%20single%20act%20of%20retaliation%2C%20but%20rather%20the%20US%20response%20will%20have%20multiple%20layers%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20first%20thing%20you%20see%20won't%20be%20the%20last%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%20Kirby%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fbriefing-room%2Fpress-briefings%2F2024%2F01%2F31%2Fpress-briefing-by-press-secretary-karine-jean-pierre-and-nsc-coordinator-for-strategic-communications-john-kirby-44%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20a%20Jan.%2031%20briefing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Jan.%2028%20attack%20marked%20the%20first%20American%20fatalities%20since%20mid-October%2C%20when%20Iran-backed%20militias%20began%20relentlessly%20attacking%20US%20forces%20across%20Iraq%20and%20Syria%20and%20is%20a%20significant%20escalation%20from%20the%20previous%20incidents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Pentagon%20has%20retaliated%20on%20a%20handful%20of%20occasions%20to%20these%20attacks%20%E2%80%94%20which%20total%20more%20than%20160%20and%20have%20featured%20a%20mix%20of%20drones%2C%20rockets%2C%20and%20missiles%20%E2%80%94%20by%20conducting%20strikes%20targeting%20Tehran-linked%20assets%20in%20Iraq%20and%20Syria.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnalysts%20at%20the%20Institute%20for%20the%20Study%20of%20War%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.un