u%20to%20see%20each%20individual%20hair%20more%20clearly%2C%20as%20well%20as%20two%20speed%20settings.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20I%20haven't%20personally%20tried%20this%20particular%20bikini%20hair%20removal%20product%20yet%2C%20over%209%2C900%20reviewers%20on%20Amazon%20agree%20the%20handheld%20mechanical%20device%20is%20beginner-friendly%20and%20gentle%20on%20the%20skin.%20This%20is%20partially%20due%20to%20its%20massage%20rollers%2C%20a%20feature%20that%20gently%20stimulates%20and%20massages%20skin%20for%20maximum%20comfort%20during%20what%20could%20otherwise%20be%20a%20slightly%20uncomfortable%20process.%20The%20device%20can%20also%20be%20used%20in%20the%20shower%20where%20warm%20water%20can%20help%20minimize%20user%20discomfort.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Braun%20Epilator%20Silk-Epil%203%20costs%20just%20under%20%2440%20on%20Amazon%2C%20which%20is%20a%20lower%20price%20than%20others%20on%20the%20market%2C%20according%20to%20my%20research.%20Because%20of%20its%20unique%20features%20and%20customer%20feedback%2C%20I%20think%20it's%20safe%20to%20say%20this%20is%20a%20good%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20laser%3A%20Tria%20Beauty%20Hair%20Removal%20Laser%204X%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tria%20Beauty%20Hair%20Removal%20Laser.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6112b41ff654ef0018416cb8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Tria%20Beauty%20Hair%20Removal%20Laser%204X%20is%20designed%20by%20dermatologists%20and%20is%20powered%20by%20the%20same%20advanced%20technology%20used%20in%20in-office%20treatments%20%E2%80%94%20making%20it%20one%20of%20the%20best%20bikini%20hair%20removal%20products.%20While%20epilators%20use%20tiny%20tweezers%20to%20pluck%20hairs%20from%20their%20roots%2C%20lasers%20target%20melanin%20at%20the%20root%20of%20the%20hair%20follicles%20to%20permanently%20disable%20regrowth%20over%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20maximum%20results%2C%20the%20Tria%20should%20be%20used%20every%20two%20weeks%20for%20a%20minimum%20of%20eight%20treatments%20in%20the%20desired%20area.%20As%20far%20as%20I%20can%20tell%2C%20the%20only%20major%20caveat%20to%20the%20Tria%20is%20its%20price.%20The%20device%20retails%20for%20%24499%2C%20however%2C%20a%20single%20laser%20hair%20removal%20treatment%20performed%20by%20a%20dermatologist%20can%20cost%20that%20much%20or%20more%20(and%20that%20price%20doesn't%20include%20follow-ups).%20So%20while%20it%20is%20pricey%2C%20that%20one-time%20cost%20gets%20you%20an%20at-home%20treatment%20you%20can%20use%20over%20and%20over%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20vegan%3A%20WooWoo%20Tame%20It!%20Vegan%20In-Shower%20Hair%20Removal%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hand%20holding%20a%20bottle%20of%20WooWoo%20Hair%20Removal%20cream%20inside%20a%20circular%20frame.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62f69415f16a0d0018e65782%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EWooWoo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20case%20you're%20unfamiliar%20with%20the%20British%20label%2C%20Woo%20Woo%20is%20an%20underrated%20brand%20for%20the%20best%20bikini%20removal%20products%20I'd%20like%20to%20bring%20to%20light.%20Its%20products%20range%20from%20intimate%20care%20to%20intimate%20hair%20removal%2C%20including%20the%20award-winning%20Tame%20It!%20In-Shower%20Hair%20Removal%20Cream.%20The%20formula%20is%20certifiably%20vegan%20and%20contains%20Aloe%20Vera%20and%20Jojoba%20Oil%20to%20ensure%20even%20the%20most%20sensitive%20skin%20types%20won't%20experience%20irritation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cream%20comes%20conveniently%20packaged%20in%20a%20shampoo-esque%20bottle%2C%20so%20you%20already%20know%20it%20will%20fit%20on%20your%20shower%20shelf.%C2%A0%20That%20said%2C%20you%20dispense%20the%20product%20by%20squeezing%20the%20bo