o%20touch-ups%20can%20be%20made%20quickly%20anywhere%2C%20at%20any%20time.%20Simply%20pop%20up%20the%20adjustable%20built-in%20trimmer%20and%20bikini%20comb%20to%20maintain%20the%20desired%20length%20around%20those%20sensitive%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20disposable%20razor%3A%20BIC%20Soleil%20Escape%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Oblong%20package%20of%20four%20Soleil%20Escape%20Bic%20disposable%20razors.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62f694fe306b6300192aa4a9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20experience%2C%20disposable%20razors%20are%20either%20surprisingly%20effective%20or%20complete%20garbage%20%E2%80%93%20with%20no%20in-between.%20BIC's%20Soleil%20Escape%2C%20however%2C%20exceeded%20my%20expectations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20looking%20for%20an%20affordable%20bikini%20hair%20removal%20tool%20that%20won't%20break%20the%20bank%20or%20scratch%20up%20your%20skin%2C%20BIC's%20new%20disposable%20four-blade%20razor%20is%20the%20answer.%20Each%20razor%20comes%20with%20a%20moisture%20strip%20that%20is%20infused%20with%20100%25%20natural%20almond%20oil%20to%20ensure%20a%20smoother%2C%20much%20more%20comfortable%20shave.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20this%20doesn't%20mean%20you%20should%20be%20any%20less%20careful%20when%20gliding%20over%20such%20a%20sensitive%20area%20with%20something%20as%20sharp%20as%20a%20blade.%20You%20should%20still%20exercise%20caution%2C%20warns%20one%20reviewer%2C%20who%20admitted%20they%20%26quot%3Bdid%20cut%20my%20leg%20a%20bit%20deep%20when%20shaving%20(my%20technique%20was%20a%20bit%20off%20when%20switching%20positions).%26quot%3B%20However%2C%20they%20did%20add%20that%20the%20razor's%20sharpness%20is%20a%20plus%20and%20that%20their%20sensitive%20skin%20did%20not%20experience%20razor%20burn%20from%20the%20product.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA