ite%20being%20thin.%20I%20styled%20it%20over%20a%20cami%20and%20sleep%20shorts%2C%20and%20still%20felt%20warm%20enough%20on%20a%20chilly%20fall%20morning.%20It%20can%20even%20easily%20pass%20as%20a%20long%20cardigan%20if%20you%20take%20out%20its%20belt.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShedding%20is%20natural%20with%20new%20cashmere%2C%20and%20because%20I%20chose%20black%2C%20it%20was%20immediately%20noticeable%20on%20my%20first%20wear.%20But%20after%20a%20few%20wears%2C%20the%20excess%20fibers%20thinned%20out%20and%20it%20was%20smooth%20enough%20to%20wear%20on%20bare%20skin.%C2%A0%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%94Gabrielle%20Chase%2C%20Associate%20Style%20%26amp%3B%20Beauty%20Editor%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERead%20more%20in%20our%20full%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fquince-cashmere-review%5C%22%3EQuince%20cashmere%20review%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhat%20should%20I%20look%20for%20in%20a%20bathrobe%3F%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20plenty%20of%20features%20to%20consider%20as%20you%20shop%20for%20the%20best%20robe%2C%20including%20style%2C%20fabric%2C%20breathability%2C%20and%20durability.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20kimono-style%20design%20is%20the%20standard.%20%26quot%3BKimono%20robes%20offer%20a%20classic%20tailored%20fit%2C%20with%20wrist-length%20sleeves%2C%20and%20have%20a%20streamlined%20flat%20collar%2C%26quot%3B%20Nuboer%20said.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20you%20can%20personalize%20a%20kimono-style%20robe's%20measurements%20via%20its%20waist%20tie%2C%20but%20you'll%20still%20have%20enough%20freedom%20of%20movement%20for%20tasks%20like%20putting%20on%20makeup%2C%20brewing%20coffee%2C%20or%20picking%20up%20the%20morning%20paper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20material%2C%20plush%20cotton%20terry%20allows%20you%20to%20skip%20toweling%20off%20post-shower%2C%20while%20less%20absorbent%20fabrics%20like%20waffle%20weave%20or%20silk%20require%20a%20pat-down%20first.%20The%20material%20also%20affects%20the%20warmth%20and%20breath