ught%20against%20the%20now-repealed%20three%20farm%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESatnam%C2%A0Singh%C2%A0Sandhu%C2%A0was%20nominated%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20by%20President%20of%20India%20Draupadi%20Murmu%20on%20January%2030%2C%20a%20move%20which%20caught%20everybody%E2%80%99s%20attention%2C%20as%20it%20was%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20who%20was%20the%20first%20person%20to%20congratulate%20him%20on%20X%20on%20his%20achievement.%20He%20is%20followed%20by%20PM%20Modi%20on%20X%2C%20earlier%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHailing%20from%20a%20small%20village%20Rasulpur%20in%20Ferozepur%20district%2C%20Sandhu%20comes%20from%20a%20family%20of%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20many%20people%20know%20that%C2%A0Satnam%C2%A0Sandhu%E2%80%99s%20brother%20Furman%C2%A0Singh%C2%A0Sandhu%C2%A0is%20the%20president%20of%20Bharti%20Kisan%20Union%2C%20Punjab%2C%20which%20is%20a%20member%20of%20SKM%2C%20that%20led%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%20and%20forced%20the%20Modi%20government%20to%20repeal%20the%20three%20farm%20laws%20in%202021.%20An%20elated%20Furman%C2%A0Sandhu%C2%A0said%20that%20all%20the%2032%20farmer%20unions%20under%20the%20SKM%20have%20congratulated%20him%20on%20his%20brother%E2%80%99s%20stupendous%20rise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAbout%C2%A0Satnam%C2%A0Singh%C2%A0Sandhu%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20typical%20rags%20to%20riches%20story%2C%C2%A0Sandhu%C2%A0has%20been%20a%20staunch%20follower%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%20So%20much%20so%20that%20all%20his%20social%20media%20accounts%20were%20flooded%20with%20photographs%20and%20videos%20of%20PM%20Modi%20and%20his%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20also%20running%20two%20NGOs%20namely%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Indian%20Minorities%20Foundation%20and%20the%20New%20India%20Foundation%20(NID)%20%E2%80%93%20both%20based%20in%20Delhi%2C%20aimed%20at%20promoting%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20initiatives%20and%20communal%20harmony.%20Sandhu%20has%20been%20leading%20different%20philanthropic%20works%20and%20providing%20financial%20assistance%20to%20many%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20child%2C%20he%20struggled%20to%20attain%20education%20but%20he%20grew%20up%20to%20become%20the%20president%20of%20Guru%20Nanak%20College%20in%20Moga%20district.%20During%20his%20struggle%20days%2C%20he%20along%20with%20his%20friends%20even%20ran%20a%20car%20sale%20purchase%20business%2C%20which%20yielded%20good%20results%20opening%20doors%20to%20further%20opportunities.%20As%20per%20Sukh%20Gill%20Moga%2C%20a%20farmer%20leader%2C%20Satnam%20Sandhu%20also%20remained%20close%20to%20Shiromani%20Akali%20Dal%20(SAD)%20leader%20and%20ex-minister%20Jathedar%20Tota%20Singh%2C%20who%20taught%20him%20lessons%20in%20politics%20and%20public%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESandhu%C2%A0launched%20the%20Chandigarh%20Group%20of%20Colleges%20at%20Landran%20village%20in%20Mohali%20district%20near%20Chandigarh%20in%202001.%20Later%20he%20formed%20Chandigarh%20University%20in%202012.%20Within%20a%20span%20of%2010%20years%2C%20Chandigarh%20University%20found%20a%20place%20in%20QS%20World%20Rankings%202023%2C%20making%20it%20first%20among%20private%20universities%20in%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20Chandigarh%20University%20hit%20the%20national%20headlines%20in%202022%2C%20when%20a%20female%20hosteller%20was%20arrested%20over%20complaints%20by%20fellow%20hostellers%20that%20she%20had%20been%20recording%20their%20videos%20in%20the%20hostel%20washrooms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFurman%20Singh%20Sandhu%2C%20president%20of%20BKU%2C%20Punjab%20lauds%20PM%20Modi%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%C2%A0Satnam%C2%A0Singh%C2%A0Sandhu%C2%A0was%20not%20available%20for%20comments%20despite%20repeated%20attempts%20by%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20his%20brother%20Furman%C2%A0Singh%C2%A0Sandhu%C2%A0spoke%20at%20length%20about%20various%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F02213141%2FGFEsqFUaUAAB3Hn.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F02213141%2FGFEsqFUaUAAB3Hn.jpg%201000w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F02213141%2FGFEsqFUaUAAB3Hn-300x176.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F02213141%2FGFEsqFUaUAAB3Hn-425x250.jpg%20425w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-695451%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22586%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESatnam%20Singh%20Sandhu%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%20Photo%20X%20(Twitter)%2F%40narendramodi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20to%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Furman%C2%A0Singh%C2%A0said%20that%20it%20was%20a%20matter%20of%20pride%20that%20PM%20Modi%20sent%20his%20brother%20to%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20who%20was%20the%20son%20of%20a%20farmer%2C%20a%20Sikh%20face%20and%20came%20from%20a%20poor%20background.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20PM%20Modi%20is%20doing%20something%20good%2C%20I%20think%2C%20we%20should%20appreciate%20him.%20He%20expressed%20his%20large%20heartedness%20and%20repealed%20the%20three%20farm%20laws.%20My%20brother%20has%20also%20written%20a%20book%20on%20PM%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20initiatives%20and%20the%20way%20he%20has%20been%20working%20for%20the%20welfare%20of%20the%20Sikhs%20in%20the%20country%2C%20it%20is%20worth%20lauding%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20when%20asked%20that%20he%20was%20a%20member%20of%20SKM%20and%20the%20farmer%20leaders%20were%20gearing%20up%20for%20the%20February%2013%20protest%20at%20Delhi%20against%20the%20Modi%20government%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20rethink.%20PM%20Modi%20has%20honored%20my%20brother%20and%20our%20family.%20I%20am%20with%20my%20brother.%20In%20fact%20all%20the%2032%20farmer%20union%20bodies%20have%20congratulated%20us%20on%20this%20achievement.%20Moreover%2C%20it%20is%20not%20important%20to%20hold%20protests%2C%20one%20can%20get%20their%20demands%20fulfilled%20by%20being%20in%20the%20government%20too.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurman%20Singh%20said%20earlier%20that%20BKU%20Punjab%20president%20Bhupinder%20Singh%20Mann%20was%20also%20nominated%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20He%20said%20that%20all%20farmer%20union%20leaders%20have%20different%20ideologies%20and%20they%20had%20never%20interfered%20with%20anybody%E2%80%99s%20choice%20of%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20the%20India%20bloc%20has%20many%20comrades%20in%20it.%20They%20are%20political%20too.%20They%20will%20be%20going%20across%20the%20country%20to%20convey%20that%20PM%20Modi%20was%20not%20good%20for%20the%20country%2C%20then%20what%3F%20Look%20how%20Modi%20took%20difficult%20decisions%20for%20the%20betterment%20of%20the%20country%20%E2%80%93%20demonetisation%2C%20abrogation%20of%20Article%20370%20and%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20Ram%20Mandir.%20These%20are%20big%20achievements%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20listed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20query%20that%20minorities%20were%20under%20attack%20and%20Sikhs%20were%20quite%20often%20branded%20as%20Khalistanis%20and%20terrorists%20by%20the%20BJP%20leaders%2C%20Furman%C2%A0Sandhu%C2%A0said%2C%20%E2%80%9CSuch%20small%20issues%20keep%20on%20happening.%20When%20it%20comes%20to%20law%20and%20order%2C%20one%20has%20to%20take%20strict%20decisions.%20There%20are%20many%20anti-India%20forces%2C%20which%20try%20to%20weaken%20the%20country%20and%20Modi%20has%20been%20acting%20against%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20during%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%20Furman%C2%A0Singh%C2%A0Sandhu%C2%A0was%20one%20among%20those%20farmer%20union%20leaders%20who%20led%20campaigns%20across%20the%20country%20telling%20people%20to%20vote%20for%20anyone%20except%20the%20BJP.%20Furman%20had%20been%20critical%20of%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20oppressive%20approach%20towards%20the%20farmers%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESKM%20responds%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20SKM%20leader%20requesting%20anonymity%20said%20Furman%C2%A0Singh%C2%A0Sandhu%C2%A0led%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%20at%20Delhi%20borders%20and%20he%20is%20a%20member%20of%20the%20SKM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20this%20move%20has%20come%20at%20a%20time%20when%20farmers%20led%20by%20SKM%20(Apolitical)%20leader%20Jagjit%C2%A0Singh%C2%A0Dallewal%20and%20Sarwan%C2%A0Singh%C2%A0Pandher%20from%20Kisan%20Mazdoor%20Sangharsh%20Committee%20(KMSC)%20were%20gearing%20up%20for%20the%20February%2013%20protest%20at%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20been%20observing%20all%20these%20developments.%20The%20Modi%20government%20wants%20to%20create%20division%20and%20confusion%20within%20the%20SKM%20through%20this%20move.%20We%20will%20have%20to%20rethink%20this%2C%20as%20Furman%20is%20a%20member%20of%20SKM%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SKM%20leader%20also%20shared%20that%20during%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%2C%20the%20agitated%20farmers%20had%20got%20a%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20event%20at%20Chandigarh%20University%20cancelled%20at%20the%20last%20minute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPolitical%20observers%20question%20nomination%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20this%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20that%20the%20chancellor%20of%20a%20private%20varsity%20was%20nominated%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20Earlier%20the%20Aam%20Admi%20Party%20(AAP)%20government%20in%20Punjab%20had%20nominated%20Lovely%20Professional%20University%20(LPU)%2C%20Phagwara%20founder%20chancellor%20Ashok%20Mittal%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20which%20had%20led%20to%20major%20debate%20in%20the%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20political%20observers%20were%20of%20the%20view%20that%20the%20rise%20of%20private%20universities%20and%20corporate%20culture%20was%20in%20sync%20with%20the%20corporate%20style%20of%20Indian%20politics%20these%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20to%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20professor%20of%20political%20science%20from%20Panjab%20University%2C%20Chandigarh%20Professor%20Khalid%20Mohammed%20said%20that%20one%20should%20see%20the%20spirit%20of%20the%20constitution%2C%20which%20says%20that%20the%20person%20can%20be%20from%20any%20field%20but%20he%20or%20she%20should%20be%20neutral.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COver%20the%20years%2C%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20has%20become%20politically%20dead.%20It%20became%20a%20house%2C%20where%20either%20those%20who%20lost%20elections%20or%20those%20who%20aligned%20with%20the%20government%20in%20power%20were%20getting%20nominated.%20In%C2%A0Satnam%C2%A0Sandhu%E2%80%99s%20case%2C%20it%20is%20an%20example%20of%20a%20corporate%20and%20political%20lobby.%20The%20centuries%20old%20Panjab%20University%20(PU)%2C%20Chandigarh%20is%20a%20name%20to%20reckon%20with%20and%20has%20been%20performing%20far%20better%20than%20Chandigarh%20University%20but%20how%20many%20people%20from%20the%20PU%20were%20nominated%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhalid%20said%20that%20the%20government%20could%20have%20considered%20renowned%20scientists%2C%20scholars%2C%20researchers%2C%20and%20academicians%20from%20Punjab%2C%20who%20have%20decades%20of%20excellent%20work%20to%20their%20credit%20for%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20but%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20idea%20is%20to%20promote%20private%20institutions.%20%E2%80%9CSatnam%20Sandhu%20made%20it%20big%20in%20life%20by%20raising%20a%20private%20university%20but%20his%20rise%20in%20this%20field%20and%20the%20support%20for%20government%20in%20power%20was%20intermixed.%20It%20definitely%20raises%20a%20question%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERenowned%20Sociologist%20from%20Panjab%20University%2C%20Chandigarh%20Professor%20Manjit%C2%A0Singh%C2%A0said%20that%20it%20is%20hardly%20a%20secret%20that%20the%20BJP%20has%20been%20desperately%20trying%20to%20rope%20in%20Sikh%20faces%20into%20its%20party%20fold%20in%20Punjab.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThough%20Satnam%20Singh%20Sandhu%20has%20been%20nominated%20to%20Rajya%20Sabha%20by%20the%20President%20of%20India%2C%20he%20has%20been%20promoting%20Modi%20and%20the%20BJP%20on%20all%20his%20social%20media%20accounts.%20After%20his%20nomination%2C%20among%20those%20who%20first%20congratulated%20him%20was%20PM%20Modi.%20Let%20us%20not%20forget%20that%20whatever%20BJP%20does%2C%20it%20is%20political%20in%20every%20sense.%20Sandhu%E2%80%99s%20nomination%2C%20despite%20having%20been%20done%20by%20the%20President%20of%20India%2C%20is%20nothing%20but%20a%20political%20move%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProfessor%20Manjit%20also%20said%20that%20there%20were%20many%20renowned%20Sikh%20figures%2C%20scientists%20and%20educationists%20from%20renowned%20universities%20of%20Punjab%2C%20who%20could%20have%20been%20nominated%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20PM%20or%20President%20of%20India%20start%20visiting%20private%20universities%2C%20it%20gives%20legitimacy%20to%20private%20and%20corporate%20institutions.%20It%20is%20harsh%20truth%20that%20political%20parties%20need%20huge%20money%20to%20contest%20elections%20and%20supporting%20private%20ventures%20helps%20them%20in%20furthering%20their%20agendas%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706890181000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F02213534%2FEffect-96.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fsatnam-singh-sandhu-why-the-newly-nominated-rajya-sabha-mp-has-become-a-talking-point%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Punjab%20educationist%2C%20who%20was%20recently%20nominated%20to%20Rajya%20Sabha%20by%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%2C%20has%20been%20point%20of%20discussion%20both%20among%20'corporate-political'%20lobby%2