.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fsandeep-reddy-vanga-reveals-how-ranveer-singh-reacted-to-ranbir-kapoor-starrer-animal-says-he-spoke-to-me-for-almost-40-minutes%2Farticleshow%2F107368451.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107368451.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ESandeep%20Reddy%20Vanga%20questioned%20the%20need%20to%20magnify%20the%20act%20of%20a%20boy%20approaching%20a%20girl%2C%20stating%20that%20it%20is%20a%20common%20and%20acceptable%20practice%20for%20expressing%20romantic%20interest.%20He%20highlighted%20that%20Kabir%20Singh's%20approach%20was%20within%20a%20classroom%20setting%20and%20differentiated%20it%20from%20the%20character%20of%20Rahul%20in%20Darr%2C%20who%20persistently%20followed%20the%20object%20of%20his%20affection.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fsandeep-reddy-vanga-reveals-how-ranveer-singh-reacted-to-ranbir-kapoor-starrer-animal-says-he-spoke-to-me-for-almost-40-minutes%2Farticleshow%2F107368451.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BJP%20Demands%20Congress'%20Apology%20on%20MP's%20'Separate%20Country'%20Remark%20As%20Opposition%20Walks%20Out%20Over%20Jharkhand%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2F22161919%2F2020_9img22_Sep_2020_PTI22-09-2020_000056B.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EOpposition%20members%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20staged%20a%20walkout%20in%20both%20houses%20of%20Parliament%20during%20the%20first%20half%20of%20the%20session%20on%20Friday%20(February%202)%20over%20the%20delay%20in%20government%20formation%20in%20Jharkhand%20as%20Treasury%20benches%20led%20the%20charge%20against%20the%20Congress%20by%20demanding%20an%20apology%20for%20its%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20D.K.%20Suresh%E2%80%99s%20remark%20on%20a%20separate%20country%20for%20South%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20leader%20of%20the%20house%20Piyush%20Goyal%20raised%20Suresh%E2%80%99s%20statement%20from%20Thursday%20in%20which%20he%20critcised%20the%20Union%20government%20on%20Thursday%20and%20said%20that%20the%20people%20of%20South%20India%20might%20have%20to%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftax-injustice-may-compel-south-india-to-demand-a-separate-country-congress-mp-d-k-suresh%5C%22%3E%20demand%20a%20separate%20country%3C%2Fa%3E%20if%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20injustice%20of%20not%20providing%20the%20rightful%20share%20of%20taxes%20(to%20the%20southern%20states)%20continued%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDoes%20the%20unity%20of%20the%20country%20matter%20to%20the%20Congress%3F%20Does%20it%20want%20to%20divide%20the%20country%20into%20the%20north%20and%20south%3F%20I%20demand%20an%20explanation%20from%20the%20Congress%20party.%20I%20condemn%20the%20Congress%20party%E2%80%99s%20thinking%20and%20demand%20an%20apology%20from%20the%20party%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Goyal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeader%20of%20opposition%20in%20the%20house%20and%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20said%20that%20Suresh%20is%20not%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSecond%2C%20I%20saw%20on%20television%20that%20he%20said%20that%20he%20has%20not%20made%20such%20a%20statement.%20But%20if%20he%20has%20said%20so%2C%20let%20the%20Privileges%20Committee%20investigate%20him.%20Third%2C%20if%20anyone%20talks%20about%20breaking%20the%20country%20we%20will%20never%20tolerate%20it%20whether%20they%20are%20from%20our%20party%20or%20anyone%20else%E2%80%99s.%20Whether%20anyone%20says%20or%20not%2C%20I%20am%20saying%20%E2%80%93%20I%2C%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20from%20Kanyakumari%20to%20Kashmir%20this%20country%20is%20one.%20This%20is%20the%20reason%20Indira%20Gandhi%20gave%20her%20life%2C%20and%20so%20did%20Rajiv%20Gandhi.%20Will%20such%20a%20party%20ever%20talk%20about%20breaking%20this%20country%3F%20But%20what%20has%20not%20been%20said%20in%20this%20house%20should%20not%20be%20repeated%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKharge%20then%20raised%20the%20issue%20of%20government%20formation%20in%20Jharkhand%20and%20alleged%20that%20the%20Constitution%20is%20being%20destroyed%2C%20by%20not%20allowing%20the%20new%20Jharkhand%20chief%20minister%20Champai%20Soren%20(who%20took%20oath%20on%20Friday%20noon)%20to%20form%20the%20government%20immediately%20following%20the%20arrest%20of%20former%20chief%20minister%20Hemant%20Soren%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20in%20an%20alleged%20land%20scam%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20Jharkhand%20an%20issue%20has%20come%20up.%20The%20chief%20minister%20resigned%20and%20immediately%20named%20his%20successor%20and%20gave%20a%20list%20of%20his%20supporters%20including%20nearly%2043%20signatures%20and%20seven%20people%20were%20outside.%20He%20(governor%20CP%20Radhakrishnan)%20did%20not%20make%20any%20arrangement%20for%20that.%20We%20have%20been%20in%20politics%20and%20so%20have%20you.%20Usually%20what%20happens%20immediately%20is%20that%20until%20an%20alternate%20arrangement%20is%20made%2C%20he%20is%20continued%20and%20you%20call%20the%20leader%20and%20ask%20him%20to%20take%20on%20a%20vote%20of%20confidence.%20But%20in%20this%20case%20the%20governor%20has%20given%2010%20days%20time%20for%20the%20vote%20of%20confidence%20and%20today%20he%20will%20take%20oath%20at%2012.30pm.%20See%20how%20the%20Constitution%20is%20being%20destroyed%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPointing%20to%20Bihar%2C%20where%20chief%20minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20on%20Sunday%20ended%20the%20alliance%20with%20RJD%20and%20formed%20the%20JDU-BJP%20government%2C%20and%20took%20oath%20as%20the%20chief%20minister%20again%20on%20the%20same%20day%2C%20Kharge%20asked%20why%20the%20government%20formation%20is%20being%20delayed%20in%20Jharkhand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20Nitish%20Kumar%20can%20take%20oath%20in%20minutes%20in%20Bihar%20and%20he%20can%20become%20chief%20minister%20again%2C%20why%20is%20this%20happening%20in%20Jharkhand%3F%20If%20resignation%2C%20acceptance%20of%20letters%20of%20support%20and%20swearing-in%20can%20happen%20in%2012%20hours%20in%20Bihar%2C%20why%20not%20in%20Jharkhand%3F%20This%20is%20shameful.%20This%20is%20destroying%20the%20Constitution%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoyal%20then%20said%20that%20he%20was%20surprised%20that%20the%20Congress%20was%20defending%20the%20Jharkhand%20chief%20minister%20whose%20hand%20in%20a%20scam%20has%20been%20exposed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20way%20such%20a%20big%20corruption%20scam%20has%20been%20exposed%20in%20Jharkhand%20in%20which%20the%20chief%20minister%20has%20done%20a%20%3Cem%3Eghotala%20(%3C%2Fem%3Escam)%20in%20connection%20with%20land%2C%20I%20am%20surprised%20that%20the%20Congress%20is%20still%20defending%20him.%20The%20Congress%20is%20not%20saying%20anything%20against%20corruption%20and%20this%20shows%20that%20corruption%20is%20in%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99%20DNA.%20The%20conduct%20of%20the%20governor%20cannot%20be%20discussed%20in%20this%20house%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EINDIA%20alliance%20members%20then%20staged%20a%20walkout%20in%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBRS%20MP%20K.%20Keshava%20Rao%20then%20stood%20up%20and%20said%20that%20he%20had%20met%20Rajya%20Sabha%20chairman%20Jagdeep%20Dhankar%20on%20Friday%20morning%20prior%20to%20the%20session%20starting%20and%20enquired%20about%20the%20notification%20that%20stated%20that%20Soren%20wanted%20to%20continue%20as%20chief%20minister%20till%20an%20alternative%20arrangement%20is%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Constitution%20says%20that%20there%20has%20to%20be%20a%20government%20and%20the%20government%20has%20to%20be%20headed%20by%20a%20chief%20minister.%20Whether%20the%20chief%20minister%20is%20this%20man%20or%20that%20man%2C%20we%20are%20not%20bothered-whether%20Nitish%20goes%20in%205%20minutes%20or%20ten%20minutes.%20There%20was%20no%20need%20for%20them%20to%20walkout%20if%20you%20could%20tell%20us%20that%20there%20was%20a%20notification%2C%20there%20was%20a%20note%20that%20the%20particular%20chief%20minister%20who%20had%20resigned%20wants%20to%20continue%20till%20the%20next%20arrangement%20is%20made%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDhankar%20said%20that%20he%20did%20not%20say%20that%20he%20has%20the%20notification%20and%20only%20said%20that%20he%20will%20look%20into%20whether%20it%20was%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20it%20is%20not%20there%20then%20my%20point%20remains%20that%20this%20country%20has%20to%20run%20through%20a%20Constitution%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Rao.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%20the%20Treasury%20benches%20again%20attempted%20to%20deflect%20the%20issue%20by%20bringing%20up%20Suresh%E2%80%99s%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20there%20is%20the%20conduct%20of%20a%20member%20of%20the%20other%20house%20talking%20about%20breaking%20the%20country%2C%20we%20are%20being%20told%20that%20you%20cannot%20take%20it%20up%20on%20technical%20grounds.%20But%20we%20are%20happily%20discussing%20the%20conduct%20of%20a%20governor%20who%20knows%20his%20position.%20And%20the%20walkout%20is%20in%20favour%20of%20corruption%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20finance%20minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20entire%20opposition%20has%20walked%20out%20in%20favour%20of%20corruption%20rather%20than%20saying%20why%20they%20want%20to%20walkout.%20We%20cannot%20speak%20about%20the%20member%20of%20the%20other%20house%20talking%20about%20breaking%20the%20country%2C%20but%20here%20they%20are%20questioning%20the%20functioning%20of%20the%20governor.%20This%20kind%20of%20conduct%20against%20a%20constitutional%20authority%20by%20a%20party%20who%20has%20been%20in%20power%20for%2045-50%20years%20is%20despicable.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20questioning%20of%20the%20governor%E2%80%99s%20conduct%20particularly%20when%20it%20is%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20corruption%20by%20the%20Congress%20is%20astonishing%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20opposition%20MPs%20also%20staged%20a%20brief%20walkout%20over%20the%20Jharkhand%20issue%2C%20with%20the%20Treasury%20Benches%20led%20the%20charge%20against%20the%20Congress%20over%20Suresh%E2%80%99s%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20the%20charge%20was%20led%20by%20Union%20Parliamentary%20Affairs%20minister%20Pralhad%20Joshi%2C%20who%20said%20that%20Suresh%20had%20made%20the%20excuse%20of%20taxation%20and%20spoke%20about%20dividing%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20condemn%20his%20statement.%20Demanding%20the%20division%20of%20the%20Congress%20has%20been%20the%20tradition%20of%20the%20Congress.%20The%20party%20should%20explain%20its%20stand%20and%20aplogise%20to%20the%20nation%20for%20insulting%20the%20Constitution%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20asked%20for%20the%20matter%20to%20be%20sent%20to%20the%20Ethics%20Committee%20and%20demanded%20the%20Congress%20to%20act%20on%20Suresh%20and%20demanded%20an%20apology%20from%20Sonia%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20then%20staged%20a%20brief%20walkout%20ahead%20of%20the%20discussion%20on%20the%20motion%20of%20thanks%20on%20the%20President%E2%80%99s%20speech.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20tweet%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20TMC%20MP%20Derek%20O%E2%80%99Brien%20stated%20that%20the%20TMC%20had%20walked%20out%20of%20both%20houses%20over%20the%20%E2%80%9Cbrazen%20misuse%20of%20agencies%20to%20undermine%20elected%20representatives.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706887611000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2F22161919%2F2020_9img22_Sep_2020_PTI22-09-2020_000056B