%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20indeed%20no%20feeling%20of%20discrimination%20towards%20religious%20minorities%20among%20the%20common%20people%20associated%20with%20Indian%20secular%20society.%20However%2C%20animosity%20towards%20Muslims%20is%20apparent%20among%20those%20aligned%20with%20the%C2%A0Hindutva%C2%A0ideology%2C%20to%20which%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20himself%20belongs.%20This%20hostility%20is%20evident%20in%20the%20daily%20occurrence%20of%20hate%20crimes%20and%20hate%20speeches.%20Notably%2C%20this%20sentiment%20is%20now%20reflected%20in%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiabudget.gov.in%2Fdoc%2Feb%2Fsbe70.pdf%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiabudget.gov.in%2Fdoc%2Feb%2Fsbe70.pdf%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1706946831893000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw09L8D8kMZQpFKGb398k4Bh%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elatest%20budget%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20year%202024%E2%80%9325%20of%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Minority%20Affairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20time%20there%20seems%20to%20be%20a%20slight%20increase%20in%20the%20budget%20compared%20to%20the%2038%25%20cut%20in%20the%20year%202023-24.%20The%20current%20budget%20stands%20at%20Rs%203183.24%20crore%2C%20a%20slight%20uptick%20from%20last%20year%E2%80%99s%20Rs%203097.60%20crore.%20However%2C%20upon%20closer%20examination%20of%20the%20budget%20details%2C%20it%20is%20evident%20that%20allocations%20for%20crucial%20schemes%20related%20to%20skill%20development%20and%20livelihoods%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20educational%20and%20social%20upliftment%20of%20minorities%2C%20have%20been%20reduced%20this%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%E2%80%99s%20apparent%20antipathy%20towards%20madrasas%20is%20clearly%20visible%20in%20the%20budget.%20In%20the%20year%202023%E2%80%9324%2C%20the%20education%20scheme%20for%20madrasas%20and%20minorities%20was%20reduced%20by%2093%25%20to%20Rs%2010%20crore%20as%20compared%20to%20the%20previous%20year.%20This%20time%2C%20it%20has%20been%20further%20reduced%20to%20a%20mere%20Rs%202%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20budget%20for%20free%20coaching%20and%20allied%20schemes%20for%20minorities%20has%20been%20reduced%20to%20Rs%2010%20crore%20this%20time%2C%20compared%20to%20Rs%2030%20crore%20last%20year.%20There%20also%20seems%20to%20be%20an%20intention%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20government%20to%20dissuade%20enrolment%20of%20children%20from%20the%20minority%20community%20in%20schools%2C%20as%20reflected%20in%20the%20consistent%20reduction%20of%20the%20budget%20for%20pre-matric%20scholarships%20for%20minorities%20each%20year.%20In%20the%20year%202023%E2%80%9324%2C%20the%20budget%20for%20the%20pre-matric%20scholarship%20for%20minorities%20was%20kept%20at%20433%20crores%3B%20this%20time%20it%20has%20been%20reduced%20to%20326.16%20crores.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmail.google.com%2Fmail%2Fu%2F0%3Fui%3D2%26ik%3D58e76611bd%26attid%3D0.0.2%26permmsgid%3Dmsg-f%3A1789772875772785549%26th%3D18d68cf2a910f38d%26view%3Dfimg%26fur%3Dip%26sz%3Ds0-l75-ft%26attbid%3DANGjdJ-xSewEAQuWXyDaGgMtgFg9PEanBZGbyX_8Cga6XGiqcCb93bcH3jpVjHb4VXSYfNwgBbYmNjqZNlTBJe1aiDO2F_VOqemPipHmjIhHKaqoc-p01KAD83lOKK4%26disp%3Demb%26realattid%3Dii_ls3zgmeo0%5C%22%20tabindex%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22STEADY%20DECLINE%20IN%20BUDGET%20FOR%20MINORITY%20SCHEMES.png%5C%22%20data-bit%3D%5C%22iit%5C%22%20data-image-whitelisted%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConversely%2C%20initiatives%20such%20as%C2%A0Skill%20Development%20Initiatives%2C%C2%A0Nai%20Manzil%C2%A0%E2%80%94%20the%20Integrated%20Educational%20and%20Livelihood%20Initiative%2C%C2%A0Upgrading%20Skills%20and%20Training%20in%20Traditional%20Arts%2FCrafts%20for%20Development%C2%A0(USTTAD)%2C%C2%A0Scheme%20for%20Leadership%20Development%20of%20Minority%20Women%2C%C2%A0Hamari%20Dharohar%20for%20conservation%20and%20protection%20of%20culture%20and%20heritage%20of%20minoritie