uld%20ever%20be%20the%20same%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20ensuing%20period%2C%20Australia%20replaced%20the%20West%20Indies%20as%20cricket%E2%80%99s%20uncontested%20behemoth.%20Building%20one%20formidable%20team%20after%20another%20and%20beating%20everything%20and%20everyone%20that%20came%20their%20way%2C%20Australia%20became%20the%20gold%20standard%20for%20quality%20in%20international%20cricket.%20And%20despite%20their%20unchallenged%20domination%20having%20ended%20for%20some%20time%20now%2C%20Australia%20remains%20the%20barometer%20to%20measure%20teams%20against%20in%20popular%20perception.%20Beating%20Australia%20in%20a%20Test%20match%20in%20their%20backyard%20continues%20to%20be%20among%20the%20hardest%20challenges%20in%20contemporary%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWest%20Indies%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20kept%20plummeting%20with%20every%20generation%20and%20comprehensively%20lost%20their%20reputation%20as%20an%20elite%20cricketing%20powerhouse.%20A%20combination%20of%20economic%2C%20logistical%2C%20and%20political%20challenges%20meant%20they%20failed%20to%20harness%20talent%20and%20protect%20the%20best%20prospects%20from%20the%20lure%20of%20T20%20franchise%20markets.%20The%20Test%20team%20as%20a%20result%20remained%20of%20considerably%20compromised%20standards%20and%20it%20kept%20reflecting%20in%20results%20that%20exponentially%20worsened.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20no%20less%20than%2027%20years%20for%20the%20West%20Indies%20to%20register%20a%20Test%20match%20win%20in%20Australia%20since%20that%20last%20one%20at%20Perth.%20It%20took%20nothing%20less%20than%20a%20miracle%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.espncricinfo.com%2Fseries%2Fwest-indies-in-australia-2023-24-1375837%2Faustralia-vs-west-indies-2nd-test-1375846%2Fmatch-report%5C%22%3EShamar%20Joseph%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20young%20Guyanese%20tearaway%20quickly%20ran%20through%20the%20formidable%20Australian%20lineup%20at%20the%20Gabba%20of%20all%20places.%20Joseph%20had%20no%20business%20even%20bowling%20in%20the%20fourth%20innings%20of%20the%20Test%20after%20he%E2%80%99d%20gone%20off%20the%20ground%20limping%20the%20previous%20night%20having%20had%20his%20toe%20sliced%20open%20by%20a%20Mitchell%20Starc%20fireball.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20being%20relegated%20to%20the%20dugout%20as%20his%20team%20hopelessly%20strolled%20through%20another%20predictably%20boring%20beatdown%20was%20not%20how%20Joseph%20was%20going%20to%20let%20his%20introduction%20to%20Test%20cricket%20finish.%20He%20took%20on%20the%20field%20and%20delivered%20a%20relentlessly%20long%20spell%20of%20serious%20fast%20bowling.%20He%20kept%20rattling%20one%20Australian%20batter%20after%20another%20and%20a%20couple%20of%20hours%20later%20had%20scripted%20his%20team%20their%20finest%20win%20of%20the%2021st%20century.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWitnessing%20this%20moment%20from%20three%20different%20commentary%20boxes%20at%20the%20Gabba%20were%20Brian%20Lara%2C%20Carl%20Hooper%2C%20and%20Ian%20Bishop.%20Each%20working%20as%20a%20guest%20commentator%20for%20different%20networks%20on%20the%20tour%20would%E2%80%99ve%20settled%20for%20a%20West%20Indies%20performance%20that%20was%20less%20humiliating%20than%20the%20previous%20one.%20It%E2%80%99s%20long%20been%20the%20story%20of%20their%20tours%20down%20under.%20Words%20failed%20as%20each%20of%20them%20struggled%20to%20succinctly%20articulate%20the%20magnitude%20of%20their%20feeling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F02175625%2FGFGZEjnXUAAbA07.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F02175625%2FGFGZEjnXUAAbA07.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F02175625%2FGFGZEjnXUAAbA07-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F02175625%2FGFGZEjnXUAAbA07-1024x576.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-695424%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EWest%20Indies%20cricket%20team.%20Photo%3A%20X%20(Twitter)%2F%20%40MacronSports.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cricketing%20journey%20between%20these%2027%20years%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20drifted%20further%20apart%20for%20these%20two%20nations.%20The%20two%20men%20in%20charge%20of%20things%20in%20the%20final%20moments%20of%20the%20Gabba%20Test%20perfectly%20embody%20this%20difference.%20Steven%20Smith%2C%20the%20one%20man%20who%20came%20painfully%20close%20to%20deny%20the%20West%20Indies%20a%20stupendous%20win%20is%20among%20Australia%E2%80%99s%20greatest%20Test%20cricketers.%20He%E2%80%99s%20reached%20where%20he%20has%20because%20a%20ruthlessly%20professional%20system%20ensures%20there%20are%20the%20fewest%20possible%20barriers%20in%20his%20potential%20translating%20to%20success.%20In%20his%2015th%20year%20playing%20international%20cricket%2C%20and%20as%20a%20100-Test%20veteran%20now%2C%20Smith%20continues%20to%20take%20great%20pride%20in%20being%20obsessed%20with%20the%20nuances%20of%20his%20batting%20because%20the%20system%20leaves%20him%20with%20little%20else%20to%20be%20worried%20about.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShamar%20Joseph%2C%20the%20other%20half%20of%20what%20the%20Gabba%20thriller%20eventually%20came%20down%20to%2C%20unfortunately%20has%20a%20far%20harsher%20reality%20to%20grapple%20with%20even%20before%20he%20can%20fully%20process%20the%20gravity%20of%20what%20he%E2%80%99s%20done.%20Far%20from%20being%20certain%20of%20pursuing%20cricket%20professionally%20less%20than%20a%20year%20ago%2C%20Joseph%E2%80%99s%20rise%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tbsnews.net%2Fsports%2Fmapping-meteoric-rise-security-guard-turned-pace-sensation-shamar-joseph-777378%5C%22%3Enothing%20short%20of%20phenomenal%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20despite%20having%20made%20headlines%20in%20every%20corner%20cricket%20reaches%2C%20Joseph%20has%20little%20to%20be%20optimistic%20about%20his%20support%20system%20lending%20him%20an%20apparatus%20that%20allows%20him%20to%20carve%20a%20Test%20career%20that%20rivals%20Smith%E2%80%99s%20(Or%20Pat%20Cummins%E2%80%99%20for%20that%20matter).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20this%20is%20where%20the%20structural%20lopsidedness%20of%20Test%20cricket%20rears%20its%20ugly%20head.%20Though%20the%20letter%20of%20the%20law%20regards%20every%20Test%20playing%20nation%20as%20equal%2C%20the%20inequalities%20are%20glaringly%20obvious.%20There%E2%80%99s%20an%20undeclared%20two-tier%20system%20in%20practice%20today%20where%20Australia%2C%20England%2C%20and%20India%20have%20grown%20increasingly%20inward-looking%20and%20are%20too%20happy%20to%20play%20between%20themselves%20while%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%20remains%20an%20avoidable%20afterthought.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20(ICC)%20has%20hardly%20shown%20any%20prudence%20in%20its%20ways%20of%20governing%20the%20sport%20and%20has%20sat%20around%20all%20too%20happily%20and%20watched%20as%20the%20three%20boards%20have%20formed%20a%20boys%E2%80%99%20club.%20The%20revenues%20generated%20from%20the%20ICC%20limited-overs%20tournaments%20are%20shared%20in%20a%20manner%20that%20belies%20a%20seriously%20run%20sport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fcricket-notions-winning-dna-choking-gene-world-cup%5C%22%3EIt%20Is%20Time%20Cricket%20Moves%20Past%20Silly%20Notions%20Of%20%E2%80%98Winning%20DNA%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Choking%20Gene%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20hosting%20Test%20matches%20has%20grown%20steadily%20unaffordable%20for%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20member%20nations.%20Every%20series%20that%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20involve%20at%20least%20one%20of%20Australia%2C%20England%2C%20or%20India%20is%20an%20extremely%20hard%20sell%20to%20earn%20broadcasters%E2%80%99%20interest.%20The%20smaller%20boards%20thus%20only%20manage%20to%20put%20together%20short%20series%20which%20pass%20by%20without%20much%20fanfare%20and%20fail%20to%20register%20as%20an%20event%20of%20note%20unless%20something%20as%20spectacular%20as%20spell%20from%20Joseph%20happens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20option%20the%20smaller%20boards%20are%20hence%20left%20with%20to%20subsist%20their%20income%20is%20to%20open%20up%20new%20revenue%20streams%20%E2%80%93%20namely%20the%20franchise%20T20%20leagues.%20With%20the%20exception%20of%20New%20Zealand%2C%20every%20country%20has%20ventured%20into%20one%20now%20and%20many%20have%20managed%20to%20attract%20capital%20from%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20owners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERunning%20and%20sustaining%20these%20leagues%20isn%E2%80%99t%20the%20easiest%20of%20propositions%20but%20for%20now%20there%20seems%20to%20be%20consensus%20among%20boards%20that%20hosting%20Test%20matches%20is%20an%20unsustainable%20exercise%20without%20being%20heavily%20subsidised%20by%20T20%20money.%20It%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20make%20for%20the%20prettiest%20of%20sights%20but%20few%20seem%20to%20have%20any%20pragmatic%20and%20scalable%20alternatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20leaves%20the%20Shamar%20Josephs%20of%20the%20world%20in%20a%20precarious%20position.%20It%E2%80%99s%20blatantly%20obvious%20that%20they%20want%20to%20play%20Tests%20that%20are%20widely%20watched%20and%20intensely%20followed.%20They%20do%20recognise%20the%20importance%20of%20cracking%20the%20format%20in%20shaping%20their%20legacy.%20Joseph%20himself%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20made%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Ftristanlavalette%2F2024%2F01%2F29%2Fshamar-joseph-commits-to-financially-stricken-test-format-after-crickets-biggest-upset%2F%3Fsh%3D53330091365a%5C%22%3Eany%20clearer%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20he%20did%20to%20the%20press%20hours%20after%20he%20bowled%20the%20house%20down%20at%20Brisbane.%20But%20unfortunately%2C%20the%20hierarchical%20order%20of%20Test%20cricket%20isn%E2%80%99t%20as%20accommodative%20of%20him%20as%20it%20is%20of%20a%20player%20of%20his%20promise%20from%20some%20of%20the%20other%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20week%20from%20Joseph%E2%80%99s%20heroics%2C%20South%20Africa%20is%20slated%20to%20play%20a%20Test%20series%20in%20New%20Zealand%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.espncricinfo.com%2Fstory%2Fa-south-africa-test-squad-with-just-seven-capped-players-1414855%5C%22%3Emassively%20depleted%20player%20pool%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Nearly%20every%20member%20of%20their%20first-choice%20squad%20remains%20occupied%20in%20SA20%2C%20the%20T20%20league%20that%E2%80%99s%20hoped%20to%20be%20the%20cash%20cow%20that%20rescues%20cricket%20in%20South%20Africa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20central%20contract%20of%20Cricket%20South%20Africa%20(CSA)%20now%20mandates%20players%20to%20remain%20available%20for%20their%20franchises.%20This%20was%20the%20most%20expected%20outcome%20of%20Indian%20cash%20flowing%20in%20but%20given%20the%20dire%20state%20of%20CSA%E2%80%99s%20finances%2C%20they%20weren%E2%80%99t%20exactly%20spoiled%20for%20choices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20traditional%20order%20where%20international%20cricket%20maintained%20its%20primacy%20has%20been%20incontrovertibly%20reversed.%20That%20the%20T20%20leagues%20offer%20a%20brand%20of%20cricket%20that%E2%80%99s%20less%20laborious%20and%20far%20more%20instantly%20gratifying%20to%20watch%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20help%20the%20longer%20formats%20either.%20With%20increasing%20inflow%20of%20private%20capital%2C%20the%20pivotal%20shift%20is%20inevitable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20absence%20of%20an%20actual%20central%20regulatory%20body%20%E2%80%93%20the%20ICC%20is%20anything%20but%20%E2%80%93%20the%20cricket%20calendar%20is%20already%20a%20mess.%20Various%20T20%20leagues%20themselves%20are%20eating%20into%20each%20other%E2%80%99s%20window%20and%20earning%20potential.%20The%20room%20for%20international%20cricket%20outside%20the%20fancier%20teams%20is%20already%20shrinking.%20And%20it%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20too%20long%20before%20more%20teams%20find%20themselves%20in%20the%20jeopardy%20South%20Africa%20are%20currently%20dealing%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithin%20a%20couple%20of%20days%20since%20his%20Gabba%20showdown%2C%20Joseph%20has%20bagged%20two%20T20%20deals%20in%20the%20UAE%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.espncricinfo.com%2Fstory%2Fwest-indies-bowler-shamar-joseph-lands-psl-deal-with-peshawar-zalmi-1418916%5C%22%3EPakistan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20first%20of%20which%20he%E2%80%99s%20had%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsportstar.thehindu.com%2Fcricket%2Fshamar-joseph-west-indies-vs-australia-test-win-ilt20-injury-gabba-first-in-27-years-windies%2Farticle67792057.ece%5C%22%3Elet%20go%20of%3C%2Fa%3E%20owing%20to%20the%20injury%20he%20picked.%20He%E2%80%99s%20soon%20going%20to%20be%20exposed%20to%20the%20side%20of%20cricket%20that%20offers%20far%20greater%20rewards%20for%20far%20lesser%20amount%20of%20bowling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20to%20then%20grind%20it%20out%20under%20hot%20sun%20on%20flat%20pitches%20in%20front%20of%20largely%20empty%20stands%20may%20not%20seem%20as%20lucrative%20as%20he%20perhaps%20thought%20after%20Gabba.%20Those%20travails%20do%20not%20feel%20as%20satisfying%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20validation%20that%20follows.%20The%20less%20arduous%20path%20of%20T20%20leagues%20starts%20to%20feel%20much%20more%20lucrative%20then.%20Better%20money%2C%20better%20infrastructure%2C%20better%20shot%20at%20longevity%2C%20lesser%20risk%20of%20career-threatening%20injuries%2C%20and%20the%20only%20real%20downside%20is%20upsetting%20a%20handful%20few%20old-school%20traditionalists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20not%20like%20players%20are%20unaware%20of%20what%20not%20preferring%20Tests%20does%20to%20how%20their%20careers%20will%20be%20written%20about.%20They%E2%80%99re%20still%20choosing%20to%20jump%20over%20to%20the%20other%20side%20because%20the%20system%20actively%20pushes%20them%20to.%20Shamar%20Joseph%20has%20made%20it%20abundantly%20clear%20what%20playing%20Test%20cricket%20for%20the%20West%20Indies%20means%20to%20him.%20But%20it%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20long%20before%20it%20dawns%20on%20him%20that%20Test%20cricket%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20quite%20value%20him%20the%20same%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20if%20he%E2%80%99s%20indeed%20forced%20to%20take%20the%20plunge%20some%20day%20and%20move%20over%20to%20the%20greener%20pastures%20of%20T20%20markets%2C%20the%20cricketing%20world%20will%20fawn%20momentarily.%20Some%20sanctimonious%20word%20salad%20shall%20follow%20reminiscing%20the%20golden%20days%20of%20West%20Indies%20cricket.%20But%20beyond%20the%20rhetoric%2C%20there%E2%80%99ll%20be%20few%20meaningful%20changes.%20And%20before%20we%20know%2C%20there%E2%80%99ll%20be%20another%20Ashes%20underway.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fparthpandya%5C%22%3EParth%20Pandya%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20an%20Ahmedabad-based%20freelance%20sports%20writer.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706877909000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F02175341%2FEffect-94.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fshamar-joseph-embodies-inherent-joy-and-systemic-fault-lines-of-test-cricket%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22There%E2%80%99s%20an%20undeclared%20two-tier%20system%20in%20practice%20where%20Australia%2C%20England%2C%20and%20India%20have%20grown%20increasingly%20inward-looking%20and%20are%20too%20happy%20to%20play%20between%20themselves%20while%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%20remains%20an%20avoidable%20afterthought.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fshamar-joseph-embodies-inherent-joy-and-systemic-fault-lines-of-test-cricket%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%2