20of%20devout%20Hindus%20go%20to%20these%20temples%20every%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAre%20these%20the%20crores%20of%20Hindus%20who%20have%20allegedly%20lost%20their%20way%3F%20No.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECrores%20of%20Hindu%20shopkeepers%20dedicate%20a%20little%20alcove%20to%20their%20preferred%20deity%20even%20in%20the%20tiniest%20of%20shops%2C%20and%20the%20day%E2%80%99s%20work%20begins%20with%20a%20prayer%20and%20the%20ritual%20tinkling%20of%20a%20bell.%20Crores%20of%20Hindus%20have%20%E2%80%98mandirs%E2%80%99%20in%20their%20homes%20%E2%80%93%20some%20modest%2C%20some%20grand%20%E2%80%93%20and%20there%20too%2C%20the%20average%20Hindu%20family%20performs%20regular%20%E2%80%98aarti%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98puja%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAre%20these%20the%20Hindus%20who%20have%20lost%20touch%20with%20their%20religion%3F%20No.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESorry%2C%20Hindus%20have%20not%20%E2%80%98lost%E2%80%99%20their%20way%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECrores%20of%20Hindus%20follow%20the%20rituals%20laid%20down%20for%20key%20moments%20of%20a%20Hindu%E2%80%99s%20life%2C%20such%20as%20the%20birth%20and%20naming%20of%20a%20child%2C%20marriage%2C%20the%20entry%20into%20a%20new%20home%2C%20and%20death%2C%20every%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAre%20these%20not%20practising%2C%20god-fearing%20Hindus%3F%20Yes%2C%20they%20most%20certainly%20are.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20then%2C%20where%20are%20the%20%E2%80%98lost%E2%80%99%20Hindus%20that%20need%20%E2%80%98re-awakening%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98de-colonising%E2%80%99%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ram%20Mandir%20in%20Ayodhya%20has%20been%20a%20well-executed%2C%20well-milked%20political%20project.%20The%20idea%20being%20to%20harvest%20votes%20from%20a%20sense%20of%20%E2%80%98resurgent%E2%80%99%20Hindu%20pride%2C%20derived%20from%20the%20construction%20of%20a%20grand%20Ram%20Mandir%2C%20allowing%20all%20the%20credit%20to%20accrue%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20hoping%20it%20translates%20into%20a%20win%20in