rther%2C%20the%20state%20governments%20give%20taxes.%20Centre%20does%20not%20have%20its%20area%20to%20extract%20taxes.%20The%20tax%20money%20that%20goes%20from%20here%20is%20distributed%20to%20us%20by%20the%20Finance%20Commission.%20Now%20injustice%20has%20happened%20to%20us%20in%20tax%20distribution.%20Devolution%20of%20taxes%20is%20not%20happening%20properly.%20There%20was%201.07%25%20decrease%20in%20devolution%20of%20taxes%20from%2014th%20finance%20commission%20to%2015th%20finance%20commission.%20It%20happened%20during%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20tenure%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20(Karnataka)%20are%20No.2%20in%20the%20country%20in%20tax%20collection%20after%20Maharashtra.%20Yet%2C%20injustice%20is%20happening%20to%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706869850000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F10%2F04155220%2FScreen-Shot-2019-10-04-at-3.51.59-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftax-injustice-may-compel-south-india-to-demand-a-separate-country-congress-mp-d-k-suresh%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22He%20criticised%20the%20BJP-led%20Union%20government%2C%20highlighting%20the%20significant%20tax%20contributions%20from%20Karnataka%20but%20inadequate%20returns.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftax-injustice-may-compel-south-india-to-demand-a-separate-country-congress-mp-d-k-suresh%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Asteroid%20the%20size%20of%20a%20skyscraper%20to%20pass%20close%20to%20Earth%20today%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706869320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F02%2F768x432%2Fskynews-asteroid-space_6441595.jpg%3F20240202104443%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fasteroid-the-size-of-a-skyscraper-to-pass-close-to-earth-today-13062015%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20asteroid%20the%20size%20of%20a%20skyscraper%20will%20pass%20close%20to%20the%20Earth%20today%20-%20cosmically%20speaking.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A313%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fasteroid-the-size-of-a-skyscraper-to-pass-close-to-earth-today-13062015%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fasteroid-the-size-of-a-skyscraper-to-pass-close-to-earth-today-13062015%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fasteroid-the-size-of-a-skyscraper-to-pass-close-to-earth-today-13062015%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watching%20the%20Steady%20Decline%20of%20Academic%20Freedom%20at%20IIM%20Ahmedabad%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F01%2F14194459%2Fimage-8.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20seventh%20consecutive%20academic%20year%20when%20I%20would%20have%20gone%20as%20a%20visiting%20faculty%20member%20to%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Management%20at%20Ahmedabad%20to%20teach%20an%20elective%20course%20on%20%E2%80%98Transformational%20Social%20Movements%E2%80%99%20to%20the%20second%20year%20of%20Post%20Graduate%20Programme%20students.%20But%20the%20invitation%20has%20not%20come%20so%20far%20and%20it%20looks%20like%20it%20is%20the%20end%20of%20my%20teaching%20stint%20at%20IIM%2C%20at%20least%20so%20long%20as%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20remains%20in%20power%20at%20the%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20had%20got%20an%20inkling%20of%20things%20to%20come%20even%20during%20my%20month-long%20last%20stay%20on%20campus%20during%20June-July%2C%202023.%20For%20the%20first%20time%2C%20guests%2C%20including%20a%20retired%20high%20court%20judge%2C%20were%20not%20allowed%20to%20enter%20the%20campus%20to%20meet%20me.%20A%20Harvard%20scholar%20was%20told%20that%20he%20could%20enter%20the%20campus%20only%20on%20the%20condition%20that%20he%20would%20not%20see%20me.%20I%20had%20to%20take%20a%20film-making%20team%20which%20had%20arrived%20from%20Mumbai%2C%20after%20they%20waited%20at%20the%20main%20gate%20for%20more%20than%20a%20couple%20of%20hours%20on%20a%20rainy%20day%2C%20to%20conduct%20an%20interview%20on%20the%20practice%20of%20prostitution%20by%20a%20community%20in%20a%20village%20in%20my%20work%20area%20as%20an%20activist%20in%20Hardoi%20district%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20to%20Ahmedabad%20Management%20Association%20campus%20across%20the%20road%20from%20the%20IIM%20old%20campus.%20I%20was%20told%20by%20the%20chief%20administrative%20officer%20of%20IIM%20Ahmedabad%20that%20this%20could%20not%20be%20considered%20an%20academic%20activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20argument%20was%20that%20I%20was%20invited%20to%20teach%20this%20course%20because%20of%20my%20experience%20as%20a%20grassroots%20activist%20and%20hence%20for%20me%20it%20was%20part%20of%20my%20academic%20activity.%20To%20bolster%20my%20argument%20I%20also%20told%20him%20that%20I%20could%20use%20the%20film%20in%20my%20class%20one%20day%2C%20when%20it%20is%20made%2C%20in%20a%20session%20on%20women%E2%80%99s%20rights.%20But%20he%20would%20not%20listen%20to%20any%20reason.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20invited%20filmmaker%20Bedabrata%20Pain%2C%20a%20former%20distinguished%20NASA%20scientist%20who%20was%20visiting%20from%20the%20United%20States%2C%20to%20screen%20a%20film%20about%20the%20impact%20of%20neoliberal%20economic%20policies%20on%20American%20farmers%20and%20connecting%20it%20to%20the%20Indian%20farmers%E2%80%99%20movement%20against%20the%20three%20laws%20in%202020-21.%20Peasants%E2%80%99%20movements%20are%20a%20topic%20formally%20covered%20in%20the%20course.%20However%2C%20the%20permission%20to%20screen%20the%20documentary%20was%20withdrawn%2C%20with%20only%20an%20interaction%20with%20the%20filmmaker%20allowed%20for%20students.%20I%20was%20also%20told%20that%20only%20students%20registered%20for%20the%20course%20could%20attend%20such%20an%20interaction.%20In%20the%20past%20I%E2%80%99ve%20been%20inviting%20scholars%20and%20students%20even%20from%20outside%20the%20IIM%20for%20open%20discussions%20on%20topics%20covered%20during%20the%20course%20and%20even%20outside%20of%20it%2C%20as%20I%20thought%20it%20provided%20a%20broader%20perspective%20to%20students.%20It%20is%20quite%20common%20for%20even%20unenrolled%20students%20to%20sit%20in%20the%20class%20of%20a%20popular%20professor%20in%20universities%20abroad.%20The%20idea%20of%20using%20boundary%20wall%20and%20security%20at%20the%20gates%20to%20prevent%20an%20interaction%20between%20the%20outside%20world%20and%20academic%20institutions%20would%20be%20considered%20juvenile%20and%20scoffed%20at%20in%20western%20institutions.%20Compare%20this%20to%20the%20Berkeley%20campus%20of%20the%20University%20of%20California%2C%20where%20any%20outsider%20can%20set%20up%20a%20table%20and%20say%20and%20distribute%20absolutely%20any%20material%20everyday%20at%20Sproul%20Plaza.%20The%20famed%20free%20speech%20movement%20in%20the%201960s%20earned%20this%20right%20on%20this%20campus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Many%20Instances%20of%20Academic%20Un-Freedom%20in%20India%20Stem%20From%20Rising%20Hindu%20Nationalism%3A%20Report%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmany-instances-of-academic-un-freedom-in-india-stem-from-rising-hindu-nationalism-report%5C%22%3EMany%20Instances%20of%20Academic%20Un-Freedom%20in%20India%20Stem%20From%20Rising%20Hindu%20Nationalism%3A%20Report%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%E2%80%99ve%20not%20known%20the%20restraints%20now%20being%20imposed%20on%20the%20academic%20freedom%20to%20exist%20on%20the%20IIM%20campus%20during%20the%20last%20five%20years%2C%20since%20I%20taught%20here%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%202018.%20When%20I%20came%20here%20to%20teach%2C%20initially%20I%20was%20apprehensive.%20This%20was%20the%20first%20time%20I%20was%20teaching%20at%20an%20IIM%20and%20my%20impression%20of%20the%20Ahmedabad%20campus%20was%20that%20of%20an%20epitome%20of%20corporate%20culture.%20I%20had%20been%20to%20jail%20twice%20in%202003%20and%202004%20in%20a%20struggle%20of%20farmers%20against%20Coca%20Cola%20where%20the%20company%20was%20depleting%20the%20water%20table%20in%20a%20rural%20area%20of%20Mehdiganj%20in%20Varanasi.%20I%20was%20invited%20in%202005%20by%20two%20dozen%20academic%20campuses%20and%20communities%20in%20North%20America%20to%20share%20experiences%20from%20the%20movement%2C%20including%20at%20Georgia%20Tech%20in%20Atlanta%2C%20which%20houses%20the%20international%20headquarters%20of%20this%20soft%20drink%20manufacturer%2C%20where%20the%20head%20of%20Coca%20Cola%20Water%20Resources%20was%20also%20present%20in%20the%20meeting.%20Free%20discussion%20in%20US%20academic%20institutions%20was%20possible%20until%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20ongoing%20Israel-Hamas%20war%20but%20India%20had%20started%20changing%20much%20before%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20was%20expelled%20from%20Banares%20Hindu%20University%20in%202016%20because%20I%20had%20decided%20to%20screen%20the%20documentary%20%3Cem%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20Daughter%3C%2Fem%3E%20produced%20by%20BBC%20after%20the%20Nirbhaya%20rape%20incident%2C%20which%20was%20banned%20by%20the%20Government%20of%20India%2C%20in%20the%20context%20of%20an%20incident%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20of%20a%20female%20student%20by%20a%20professor%20in%20the%20management%20department.%20The%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20high%20court%20had%20rejected%20the%20charges%20of%20me%20engaging%20in%20anti-national%20activities%20and%20ordered%20my%20reinstatement%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20dispute%20between%20me%20and%20university%20authorities%20arose%20because%20of%20different%20ideologies.%20The%20honourable%20judges%20quoted%20two%20amazing%20statements%20which%20summarise%20the%20judgement.%20One%20was%20by%20the%20founder%20of%20the%20university%2C%20Madan%20Mohan%20Malviya%3A%20%E2%80%9CIndia%20is%20not%20a%20country%20of%20Hindus%20only.%20It%20is%20a%20country%20of%20the%20Muslims%2C%20Christians%20and%20Parsees%20too.%20The%20country%20can%20gain%20strength%20and%20develop%20itself%20only%20when%20the%20people%20of%20different%20communities%20in%20India%20live%20in%20mutual%20goodwill%20and%20harmony.%E2%80%9D%20The%20second%20was%20a%20quote%20by%20Voltaire%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20disapprove%20of%20what%20you%20say%2C%20but%20I%E2%80%99ll%20defend%20to%20the%20death%20your%20right%20to%20say%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstitution%20after%20institution%20had%20begun%20to%20capitulate%20under%20the%20BJP%20rule%20and%20academic%20freedom%20or%20the%20fundamental%20right%20of%20freedom%20of%20expression%20was%20being%20squeezed%20out%20from%20campus%20after%20campus.%20But%20I%20used%20to%20boast%20to%20my%20friends%20that%20IIM%20Ahmedabad%20had%20a%20strong%20culture%20of%20autonomy%20and%20decentralised%20decision%20making.%20For%20example%2C%20at%20other%20institutions%20where%20I%20had%20taught%2C%20I%20had%20to%20meet%20the%20director%20to%20finalise%20my%20assignment%20%E2%80%93%20but%20at%20IIM%20Ahmedabad%20I%20met%20the%20then%20director%2C%20Errol%20D%E2%80%99Souza%2C%20by%20chance%20in%20my%20fifth%20year%20of%20teaching%2C%20as%20we%20happened%20to%20be%20teaching%20in%20neighbouring%20classrooms%20and%20we%20were%20face%20to%20face%20during%20a%20simultaneous%20tea%20break.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20centralisation%20in%20decision%20making%20at%20IIM%20Ahmedabad%20has%20begun%20with%20the%20change%20of%20directorship.%20The%20power%20to%20appoint%20the%20chairperson%20of%20Board%20of%20Governors%2C%20which%20until%20now%20was%20a%20prerogative%20of%20the%20Board%20only%2C%20has%20been%20usurped%20by%20the%20government%20and%20from%20now%20on%20the%20director%20will%20be%20appointed%20by%20a%20Board%20which%20will%20be%20headed%20by%20a%20person%20favourable%20to%20the%20government.%20By%20extension%2C%20the%20director%20will%20also%20be%20a%20person%20favourable%20to%20the%20government.%20In%20the%20present%20context%2C%20(s)he%20has%20to%20be%20a%20person%20who%20has%20the%20approval%20of%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20or%20its%20ideological%20parent%2C%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsewak%20Sangh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Safeguarding%20Academic%20Freedom%20Is%20the%20Bedrock%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20Constitutional%20Morality%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fsafeguarding-academic-freedom-is-the-bedrock-of-indias-constitutional-morality%5C%22%3ESafeguarding%20Academic%20Freedom%20Is%20the%20Bedrock%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20Constitutional%20Morality%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20these%20years%2C%20I%E2%80%99ve%20also%20known%20IIM%20Ahmedabad%20students%20for%20their%20steadfast%20progressive%20thinking%2C%20remaining%20immune%20to%20the%20political%20atmosphere%20in%20the%20country%2C%20compared%20to%20students%20at%20other%20institutions%20who%20appeared%20to%20be%20more%20vulnerable.%20Once%20I%20was%20told%20by%20a%20professor%20here%20that%20IIM%20Ahmedabad%20believes%20in%20exposing%20its%20students%20to%20variegated%20ideas%20and%20then%20leave%20it%20to%20their%20judgement.%20But%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20six%20years%2C%20there%20were%20murmurs%20in%20my%20class%20under%20the%20influence%20of%20the%20pervading%20ideology%20of%20religious%20nationalism.%20During%20a%20discussion%20on%20the%20right%20of%20women%20of%20menstruating%20age%20to%20enter%20the%20Sabarimala%20temple%2C%20which%20is%20backed%20by%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20judgement%2C%20a%20student%20suggested%20that%20I%20should%20not%20take%20up%20controversial%20traditional%20issues%20for%20discussion%20in%20class.%20I%20had%20to%20point%20out%20to%20this%20student%20and%20the%20class%20that%20if%20we%20were%20to%20accept%20everything%20in%20our%20tradition%20uncritically%2C%20then%20probably%20only%20Vaishya%20students%20should%20be%20studying%20at%20IIM%20and%20only%20Brahmins%20should%20be%20teaching%2C%20as%20we%20would%20have%20to%20abide%20by%20the%20caste%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecent%20incidents%20on%20the%20IIM%20Ahmedabad%20campus%20don%E2%80%99t%20bode%20well%20for%20the%20academic%20freedom%20of%20IIMs%2C%20and%20in%20general%20for%20the%20health%20of%20the%20academic%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAcademia%20is%20all%20about%20freedom%20of%20thought%20and%20an%20academic%20would%20fight%20to%20the%20last%20to%20preserve%20his%2Fher%20right.%20Only%20in%20institutions%20which%20have%20honoured%20such%20freedom%20has%20there%20been%20meaningful%20academic%20activity%20and%20true%20research.%20If%20this%20freedom%20is%20curbed%2C%20the%20tendency%20would%20be%20to%20do%20things%20which%20would%20appease%20the%20rulers%20or%20at%20least%20not%20displease%20them.%20Such%20considerations%20guiding%20academic%20activity%20would%20lead%20to%20a%20farce.%20It%20would%20be%20result%20in%20regimentation%20on%20academic%20campuses%20which%20may%20produce%20degree-holding%20individuals%20who%20would%20be%20beholden%20to%20the%20powers%20that%20be.%20They%20would%20not%20serve%20the%20larger%20humanity%20but%20only%20the%20government%20of%20the%20day%20or%20the%20dominating%20ideology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20will%20continue%20to%20fight%20for%20the%20fundamental%20right%20to%20freedom%20of%20expression%20guaranteed%20by%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%20outside%20IIM%20Ahmedabad%20now.%20My%20friends%20in%20the%20larger%20academic%20community%20have%20to%C2%A0%20stand%20up%20to%20face%20the%20assault%20on%20their%20academic%20freedom%2C%20lest%20their%20institutions%20are%20taken%20over%20by%20an%20ideology%20which%20will%20make%20free%20thinking%20subservient%20to%20authoritarian%20regime.%20The%20quality%20of%20Indian%20academic%20institutions%2C%20of%20whatever%20worth%20it%20is%2C%20cannot%20be%20pawned%20to%20a%20regressive%20ideology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESandeep%20Pandey%20is%20presently%20teaching%2