asi's%20Gyanvapi%20mosque%20after%20a%20district%20court%20yesterday%20ordered%20the%20administration%20to%20unseal%20the%20premises%2C%2030%20years%20after%20it%20was%20sealed%20on%20the%20orders%20of%20former%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Mulayam%20Singh%20Yadav%2C%C2%A0shortly%20after%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20demolition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHindu%20side%20allowed%20to%20offer%20prayers...%20district%20administration%20will%20have%20to%20make%20arrangements%20in%20seven%20days.%20Everyone%20will%20have%20the%20right%20to%20pray%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20Vishnu%20Shankar%20Jain%2C%20lawyer%20for%20the%20Hindu%20side%2C%20told%20the%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20area%20near%20the%20mosque%2C%20located%20right%20next%20to%20Kashi%20Vishwanath%20temple%2C%20witnessed%20frenetic%20activity%20late%20last%20night%20as%20Hindu%20devotees%20started%20reaching%20the%20mosque%20to%20pray%20in%20the%20cellar%2C%20named%20'Vyas%20ka%20tehkana'.%20Members%20of%20a%20Hindu%20outfit%2C%20Rashtriya%20Hindu%20Dal%2C%20were%20seen%20pasting%20the%20'mandir'%20(temple)%20word%20on%20a%20signage%20near%20the%20mosque.%20The%20puja%20started%20around%203%20am%20today.%20Heavy%20force%20has%20been%20deployed%20to%20prevent%20any%20untoward%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mosque%20has%20four%20cellars%20in%20its%20basement.%20One%20of%20them%20was%20in%20the%20possession%20of%20a%20family%20of%20priests%20that%20used%20to%20live%20there.%20Somnath%20Vyas%2C%20a%20member%20of%20Vyas%20family%2C%20offered%20prayers%20in%20the%20cellar%20before%20it%20was%20sealed%20in%201993%2C%20according%20to%20the%20petition%20by%20Shailendra%20Pathak%2C%20the%20petitioner%20and%20a%20member%20of%20the%20family.%20He%20had%20argued%20in%20court%20that%20as%20hereditary%20priests%2C%20they%20should%20be%20allowed%20to%20enter%20the%20structure%20and%20worship%20there.%20The%20court%20yesterday%20asked%20the%20district%20administration%20to%20ensure%20that%20prayers%20can%20be%20held%20inside%20the%20cellar%20within%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mosque%20committee%20has%20said%20they%20would%20be%20challenging%20the%20court's%20order%20in%20Allahabad%20High%20Court.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20happening%20to%20get%20political%20advantage.%20The%20same%20approach%20is%20being%20adopted%2C%20which%20was%20done%20in%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20case%2C%26quot%3B%20their%20counsel%20Merajuddin%20Siddiqui%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYesterday's%20order%20is%20being%20seen%20as%20a%20major%20development%20in%20the%20Gyanvapi%20case%2C%20in%20which%20Hindu%20petitioners%20have%20sought%20permission%20to%20pray%20in%20the%20mosque%20complex.%20The%20Archaeological%20Survey%20of%20India%2C%20which%20conducted%20a%20survey%20of%20the%20premises%2C%20has%20shared%20its%20report%20with%20the%20petitioners%20and%20the%20mosque%20committee.%20The%20report%20concluded%20that%20a%20large%20Hindu%20temple%20existed%20on%20the%20site%20before%20the%20mosque%20was%20built.%20Four%20Hindu%20women%20have%20now%20moved%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20seeking%20the%20excavation%20and%20scientific%20survey%20of%20a%20section%20that%20had%20been%20sealed%20by%20a%20court%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20has%20stressed%20that%20due%20process%20must%20be%20followed%20while%20implementing%20the%20court%20order.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Varanasi%20Court%20fixed%20a%207-day%20period%20for%20it.%20What%20we%20are%20seeing%20now%20is%20a%20concerted%20effort%20to%20go%20beyond%20the%20due%20process%20and%20prevent%20any%20legal%20recourse%20that%20can%20be%20taken%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20refrained%20from%20commenting%20on%20yesterday's%20development%2C%20saying%20the%20matter%20is%20subjudice.%20Hindu%20outfits%20such%20as%20the%20Vishva%20Hindu%20Parishad%20have%20welcomed%20the%20ruling.%20%26quot%3BToday%2C%20a%20court%20in%20Kashi%20has%20given%20a%20very%20important%20decision%2C%20filling