d.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20RBI%20Has%20Put%20Restrictions%20On%20Paytm%20Payments%20Bank%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RBI%20said%20it%20had%20in%20March%202022%20asked%20the%20Paytm%20Payments%20Bank%20to%20stop%20adding%20new%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20Comprehensive%20System%20Audit%20report%20and%20subsequent%20compliance%20validation%20report%20of%20the%20external%20auditors%20revealed%20persistent%20non-compliances%20and%20continued%20material%20supervisory%20concerns%20in%20the%20bank%2C%20warranting%20further%20supervisory%20action%2C%20the%20RBI%20said%2C%20without%20disclosing%20details.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20action%20against%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frbi-action-paytm-payments-bank-the-only-services-allowed-are-4967226%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPaytm%20Payments%20Bank%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20taken%20under%20Section%2035A%20of%20the%20Banking%20Regulation%20Act%2C%201949%2C%20the%20central%20bank%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Paytm%20Payments%20Bank%20Said%20On%20RBI%20Restrictions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPaytm%20Payments%20Bank%2C%20an%20associate%20of%20One%2097%20Communications%20Limited%20(OCL)%2C%20said%20it%20is%20taking%20%26quot%3Bimmediate%20steps%26quot%3B%20to%20comply%20with%20the%20RBI's%20directions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOCL%2C%20as%20a%20payments%20company%2C%20works%20with%20various%20banks%20(not%20just%20Paytm%20Payments%20Bank)%2C%20on%20various%20payments%20products%2C%20the%20fintech%20company%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EUpdate%3A%20Paytm%20Payments%20Bank%20Limited%2C%20an%20associate%20of%20Paytm%20receives%20RBI%20directions.%20Paytm%20to%20expand%20its%20existing%20relationships%20with%20leading%20third-party%20banks%20to%20distribute%20payments%20and%20financial%20services%20products.%3Cbr%3E%5CnRead%20more%20here%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FNsPCOxp6VJ%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FNsPCOxp6VJ%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FfQjozyR11m%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FfQjozyR11m%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Paytm%20(%40Paytm)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPaytm%2Fstatus%2F1752783857697665354%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%2031%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20now%20will%20accelerate%20the%20plans%20and%20completely%20move%20to%20other%20bank%20partners.%20Going%20forward%2C%20OCL%20will%20be%20working%20only%20with%20other%20banks%2C%20and%20not%20with%20Paytm%20Payments%20Bank%20Limited.%20The%20next%20phase%20of%20OCL's%20journey%20is%20to%20continue%20to%20expand%20its%20payments%20and%20financial%20services%20business%2C%20only%20in%20partnerships%20with%20other%20banks%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EPaytm%20Likely%20To%20Lose%20Over%20Rs%20500%20Crore%20Due%20To%20RBI%20Action%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPaytm%20said%20it%20expects%20a%20%26quot%3Bworst%20case%20impact%26quot%3B%20of%20Rs%20300%20crore%20to%20Rs%20500%20crore%20to%20its%20annual%20earnings%20from%20RBI's%20order%20barring%20Paytm%20Payments%20Bank%20from%20accepting%20fresh%20deposits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20company%20said%20it%20expects%20to%20%26quot%3Bcontinue%20on%20its%20trajectory%26quot%3B%20to%20improve%20its%20profitability.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706752380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fj86oub88_paytm-payments-bank_625x300_01_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpaytm-paytm-news-explained-why-rbi-has-put-restrictions-on-paytm-payments-bank-4970845%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20(RBI)%20on%20Wednesday%20ordered%20Paytm%20Payments%20Bank%20to%20stop%20accepting%20fre