%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F329201%2Fgrailmaker-innovations-vision-nanny-platform-app-solution-for-kids-cortical-visual-impairment%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20visual%20disabilities.%3C%2Fa%3E%20And%20bringing%20this%20to%20fruition%20is%20a%20school%20in%20Gandhinagar%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20setting%20the%20bar%20high%20for%20its%20inclusive%20architectural%20design.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20its%20unique%20construction%20and%20thoughtful%20design%2C%20the%20school%20empowers%20children%20to%20rely%20on%20their%20other%20senses%20to%20navigate%20through%20the%20educational%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdorned%20with%20white%20walls%20and%20airy%20courtyards%2C%20%E2%80%98The%20School%20for%20The%20Blind%20and%20Visually%20Impaired%E2%80%99%2C%20designed%20by%20SEALabs%2C%20is%20dedicated%20to%20these%20particular%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEvery%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F126863%2Fcan-help-visually-impaired-twitter-users-see-pictures-heres%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20visually%20impaired%20%3C%2Fa%3Echild%20has%20different%20needs%2C%20and%20we%20wanted%20to%20create%20a%20space%20that%20was%20inclusive%20of%20them%20all%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Anand%20Sonecha%2C%20the%20architect%20of%20SEALabs%2C%20speaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20how%20does%20this%20school%20help%20its%20children%20navigate%3F%20I%E2%80%99m%20glad%20you%20asked!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Found%20inspiration%20in%20many%20place%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnand%20started%20his%20practice%20back%20in%202015%20and%20had%20never%20worked%20on%20developing%20a%20school%20before.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20Viren%20Joshi%2C%20the%20president%20of%20the%20school%2C%20approached%20me%20to%20have%20a%20look%2C%20I%20was%20very%20honoured.%20I%20was%20excited%20to%20get%20to%20the%20school%20and%20start%20the%20designing%20process%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20the%20idea%20behind%20the%20school%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20an%20existing%20building%20but%20was%20in%20a%20bad%20condition.%20It%20was%20a%20school%20for%20underprivileged%20children%20with%20visual%20impairment.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20two%20buildings%20%E2%80%94%20one%20was%20a%20hostel%20facility%20and%20the%20other%20one%20was%20the%20school.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20each%20room%2C%20twelve%20to%20fifteen%20students%20were%20living%20in%20bunk%20beds.%20Consequently%2C%20a%20decision%20was%20made%20to%20construct%20a%20new%20academic%20building%20and%20convert%20the%20existing%20structure%20entirely%20into%20a%20hostel%20facility.%20This%20would%20allow%20for%20redistribution%20of%20students%20across%20the%20ground%20and%20first%20floors%2C%20while%20providing%20them%20with%20more%20comfortable%20and%20improved%20living%20spaces.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fschool-3-1706623026.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20School%20for%20The%20Blind%20and%20Visually%20Impaired%20is%20located%20in%20Gandhinagar%2C%20Gujarat.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fschool-3-1706623026.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fschool-3-1706623026-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fschool-3-1706623026-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fschool-3-1706623026-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fschool-3-1706623026-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-340120%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20School%20for%20The%20Blind%20and%20Visually%20Impaired%20is%20located%20in%20Gandhinagar%2C%20Gujarat.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Anand%20was%20excited%20to%20get%20on%20board%20the%20project%2C%20he%20lacked%20a%20source%20of%20inspiration.%20To%20find%20that%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20spend%20time%20with%20the%20kids.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20began%20observing%20how%20students%20navigate%20through%20different%20places%20and%20spaces%2C%20identifying%20their%20preferences%20and%20gathering%20spots.%20Additionally%2C%20I%20made%20friends%20with%20students%20to%20better%20understand%20their%20daily%20routines%2C%20likes%2C%20and%20dislikes%20within%20the%20existing%20school.%20Similarly%2C%20I%20engaged%20in%20discussions%20with%20teachers%20to%20explore%20ways%20to%20enhance%20the%20learning%20environment%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20Anand%20also%20started%20to%20visit%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F338824%2Fmuskaan-dreams-abhishek-dubey-introduces-technology-in-rural-school-education-digital-literacy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20schools%20for%20children%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20visual%20impairment%20across%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Victoria%20Memorial%20School%20for%20the%20Blind%20in%20Mumbai%20left%20a%20lasting%20impression%20on%20me%20because%20of%20its%20remarkable%20beauty%2C%20despite%20being%20an%20adaptively%20reused%20building.%20However%2C%20I%20found%20very%20few%20good%20examples%20of%20schools%20specifically%20designed%20for%20users%20with%20disabilities.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20I%20later%20volunteered%20at%20the%20Perkins%20School%20for%20the%20Blind%20in%20Massachusetts%2C%20one%20of%20the%20oldest%20schools%20in%20the%20United%20States.%20Established%20in%201829%2C%20it%20boasts%20a%20rich%20history%20with%20stalwarts%20like%20Helen%20Keller%2C%20Laura%20Bridgman%2C%20and%20Anne%20Sullivan%20who%20all%20studied%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20found%20wonderful%20mentors%20in%20the%20US%20and%20was%20able%20to%20find%20the%20right%20direction%20for%20the%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20went%20out%20looking%20for%20inspiration%2C%20I%20realised%20how%20it%20was%20not%20one%20place%20that%20could%20help%20me%20but%20a%20lot.%20Visiting%20various%20schools%20was%20a%20great%20learning%20arc%20for%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EUsing%20five%20senses%20to%20navigate%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20school%20is%20designed%20to%20be%20navigated%20with%20the%20help%20of%20four%20senses%3A%20sight%2C%20hearing%2C%20touch%2C%20and%20smell.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COnly%2015%25%20of%20people%20with%20blindness%20experience%20a%20complete%20lack%20of%20sight.%20The%20majority%20of%20individuals%20who%20are%20blind%20may%20perceive%20light%20or%20colour%2C%20and%20those%20with%20different%20impairments%20have%20varying%20degrees%20of%20usable%20vision%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fschool-4-1706623360.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20school%20walls%20have%20different%20textures%20for%20students%20to%20recognise%20the%20classes.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fschool-4-1706623360.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fschool-4-1706623360-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F