20what%20happened%20to%20her%20father%2C%20who%20immediately%20went%20to%20the%20police%2C%20who%20arrested%20the%20three%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20followed%20makes%20the%20tale%20harrowing.%20Going%20against%20the%20entire%20village%2C%20the%20film%20follows%20Ranjit%20from%20the%20time%20he%20first%20reports%20the%20crime%20and%20his%20journey%20over%2014%20months%20as%20he%20pursues%20justice%20and%20ensures%20that%20the%20criminals%20are%20brought%20to%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20documents%20how%20village%20elders%20expected%20Kiran%20to%20marry%20one%20of%20her%20abusers.%20A%20woman%20in%20the%20village%20is%20heard%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20could%20have%20been%20settled%20in%20the%20village.%20They%20already%20had%20sex%2C%20might%20as%20well%20get%20them%20married%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20shows%20the%20stark%20reality%20for%20many%20abused%20women%2C%20which%20is%20scary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgainst%20this%20backdrop%20and%20mindset%2C%20the%20relentless%20pursuit%20of%20justice%20in%20the%20face%20of%20pressure%20and%20intimidation%20to%20drop%20the%20case%20is%20worth%20every%20plaudit.%20Ranjit%2C%20his%20wife%20Jaganti%2C%20and%20Kiran%20remain%20unfazed.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20think%20of%20Kiran%2C%20every%20fear%20goes%20away%2C%E2%80%9D%20remarks%20Ranjit%20in%20the%20film.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRanjit%20simply%20refused%20to%20accept%20the%20status%20quo%20and%2C%20because%20of%20that%2C%20showed%20us%20that%20change%20is%20possible%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pahuja%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20as%20Kiran%20turned%2018%20by%20the%20time%20the%20editing%20of%20the%20documentary%20film%20was%20completed%2C%20she%20chose%20to%20come%20on%20the%20screen%2C%20not%20wanting%20to%20remain%20hidden.%20She%20wished%20to%20encourage%20other%20survivors%20through%20her%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20film%20would%20also%20connect%20with%20many%20on%20its%20quotient%20of%20resilience%20a